eals & a monthly box subscription, \"Wellybox.\"','Gilt Groupe Meets the Wellness World','[\"Los Angeles\"]','Wellyfish'),('Total Health Card is a health and wellness platform empowering consumers to live healthier lives.  THCard is a platform that provides the Total HealthScore, verified FICA like score for your health and wellness and also a community-based mobile marketplace for complementary medicine, healthy eating, beauty and cosmetics.\n\nThere is no credible solution to consistently influence healthy human behavior to help prevent chronic diseases. At the same time main stream and complementary medical providers do not have reliable and affordable way to engage and monitor their patients/clients outside of their practice. \n\nTracking, managing, and optimizing wellness without major administrative component. Total HealthScore will be a proven way that optimizes engagement. \n\nFrom the medical provider point of view, THCard lowers customer acquisition costs by providing a large group of healthcare consumers and a commission-only payment platform. \n \n ','Mint.com For Health And Fitness','[\"Denver\"]','Total Health Card'),('Coach Explore connects consumers with coaches and health providers and their events and retreats. Coach Explore gives coaches and providers a platform to expand their market and sales reach.  Our website provides simple ways for users to find, compare and hire a coach or health provider or consumers can purchase one of their products, retreats or events.Our mission is to accelerate connections and paths of discovery between individuals in self development, personal growth and well-being. \n\n','Connecting Consumers to Coaches','[\"San Francisco\"]','Coach Explore'),('Medicinal marijuana is a multi-million dollar industry in Colorado.  Colorado Springs alone has over 30 medicinal shops open today, however the majority of these shops are low-grade facilities, run by incapable or unprofessional owners/staff.  Even while lacking, patients deal with these facilities unwillingly due to a lack of local options for their needs. Sativa Medicinal Marijuana Center will change that, giving the customer the most professional experience in the alternative medicine field.','Higher standard Medicinal Marijuana shop','[\"Colorado Springs\"]','Sativa Medicinal Marijuana Center'),('Based on eastern and western medicine, NaturalTutor ONLINE \'screening\' Tests are able to give you circumstantial evidence for the detection of a primary cause of Illness.\nAnyone can check for his signs and symptoms to obtain suggestions on nutritional deficiencies, toxicities, emotional disturbances, and possible deseases. \nDoctors use NaturalTutor as a daily operative platform to manage their Patients screening information. It is an amazing tool to overview the patient.','The first Checkup online','[\"Stockholm\"]','NaturalTutor'),('The stealthvape is a portable handheld aromatherapy vaporizer that can be used with a wide variety of different vaporizable substances. At only $99 with a lifetime warranty, it is one of the cheapest battery powered vaporizers on the market and is targeting a wide range of people who wish to be able to discreetly vaporize while on the go.','Portable vaporizers and medical devices.','[\"New York City\"]','Medicinal Corp'),('Green Seed Capital is looking for those building software, products and services to serve the Medicinal Marijuana Ancillary market.','Seeking builders of services, products and software that service the MMJ Ancillary market.','[\"Seattle\"]','Green Seed Capital'),('BrainCore Marietta offers QEEG based Biofeedback (Neurofeedback) to individuals looking for alternative health care to obtain a healthier brain.  It is an in office therapy provided to any person ages 6 and up.  There is a over 40 years of research proving the efficacy of Neurofeedback.  Many symptoms of neurological disorders are caused by dysregulated brainwaves, BrainCore Marietta provides a safe comfortable place for patie