is'),('To date, most drug discovery efforts are failing because they are only able to sample a tiny portion of chemical space (protein targets); usually 1-5 million substances per project (molecules) are considered when trying to find a starting point.  Carmolex’s exclusive software, enormous virtual small molecule libraries and world-class mastery of special chemistry empower it to be the most innovative engine for drug precursor discovery commercially available. Our AnchorQueryTM  license and extensive InstantChemistryTM database make possible the design and virtual screening of today’s much more challenging chemical space (thousands of new protein targets recently discovered await intervention). Carmolex’s rational process overcomes traditional, slow, robotic screening (HTP) and the unpredictability of multi-step chemical synthesis, with smarter solutions able to increase the likelihood of successfully delivering molecules by several orders of magnitude. ','Redefining Drug Discovery','[\"Pittsburgh\"]','Carmolex'),('Novel therapeutic to improve fertility success rates in Assisted Reproductive Technologies, In Vitro Fertilization (IVF), for 15% of the Global Population who suffers from some form of infertility, (7% of couples).\nOf the 3-4 Million cycles of IVF performed globally, only 25% are successful. This novel product has the potential to induce embryonic implantation thereby improving fertility success rates to well over 50%, making it very likely for couples to achieve pregnancy.','Improved Therapy for Infertility/IVF','[\"Atlanta\"]','Incintas Therapeutics'),('The EPCC is a portable, ruggedized electrosurgical device that represents a functional enhancement over proven  RF medical technology, such as the Bovie and Plasma Blade.    EPCC offers surgeons and medical technicians the ability to bloodlessly cut, cauterize(no charring), and ablate biological tissue in wet/dry environments without external grounding pad limitations eliminating the risk of patient burns/shock.  Advantages are portability, precision control, safety, cutting bone/cartilage.','Portable Ruggedized Electrosurgical Cauterizer Cutter','[\"Houston\"]','Laverne Douglas Technologies'),('Everybody deserves a good night sleep, especially new parents. Monbaby is an active health baby monitor that helps parents to sleep better. One of the founders, as any first-time parents, remembers worrying about SIDS and not being able to fall asleep or to rest. Monbaby is designed to solve this problem, to alleviate parents anxiety about their newborns well-being.\r\nOur solution is Monbaby, an active, real-time, wireless baby heal monitor in the shape of an oval button that could be attached on almost any article of baby clothing.\r\nWe believe that a combination of conveniently attached sensor, sleep helping application and our cutting edge Bio-Data Analytics Library make this an awesome product and a killer technology suite','Sleep analyzer that helps parents of newborns to sleep','[\"North Bergen\"]','Mondevices'),('Renu is developing novel proteins to treat ischemic injury.  \n\nOur lead program, Intestinal Trefoil Factor (ITF), is a secreted protein with a known role in mucosal repair. Renu has shown that acute admin of recombinant ITF significantly reduces myocardial infarct size in a mouse model.\n\nRenu is developing recombinant human ITF for acute post-MI therapy with potential to protect the ischemic myocardium from injury and minimize cardiomyocyte death, ultimately improving outcomes for AMI patients.','Novel proteins for treatment of ischemic injury','[\"Cambridge, MA\"]','Renu Therapeutics'),('With an expanding portfolio of intellectual property and interdisciplinary technical expertise, Peptineo represents the new face of biotechnology and bioengineering. By employing a systems-based approach, Peptineo technical solutions involve drug delivery combinations including “tunable” nano-carriers, engineered peptides, re-formulated pharmaceuticals, and as ap