d life sciences industries. Marigold’s primary focus is helping clients identify or build the strategic capabilities and operational excellence necessary to drive long-term, sustainable growth.\n\nOur project experience ranges from multi-billion dollar capital projects to venture backed start-ups.','','[\"Houston\"]','Marigold Partners'),('We are a team of chemists, biologists, geneticists, and engineers who\'s goal it is to bring the industry into the 21st century by using current recombinant technologies, and sequencing methods. The goal is to produce, develop the highest quality seeds possible for a fraction of the cost than what is currently on the market. 2 types of seeds will be produced\n\n1) Seeds for business use will be modified to produce higher yield, lower maintenance, higher quality, and more variability \n\n2) Simple Seeds will be sold for personal use. These seeds will need far less maintenance compared to seeds on the current market making them easy enough for anyone to grow without restrictions. All that will be required is a pot, sunlight, soil, and water. ','Biotechnology and medicinal marijuana.','[\"Boulder\"]','AdCy Biotechnologies Inc.'),('The Nuance Designs auto injector, Fusion, is poised to change the $1B self injection device market.  The Fusion auto injector provides better safety, reliability and convenience to patients who must inject themselves with medications at home.  This new approach improves on the major drawbacks of the other devices currently available.  \n\nFusion is smaller, smoother and smarter than current auto injection technology which makes it more convenient and less intimidating to patents of all kinds.  \n\nAfter over 15 years designing the most successful self injection devices for other firms, the principles of Nuance Designs recognized the need for new innovation. Multiple patents (already applied) will result from this approach and customer reaction so far  has been great - \"That\'s brilliant. We\'ve never seen 