et of events and situations to be monitored can be defined and modified very easily, also without technical assistance. This information can be used to improve everyday life. \nSuch “detection” does not invade personal privacy, and it does not involve recording of video, sounds or images at any time.\nThe key elements of the XETAL MoCa are reliability, 24/7 operation, low-cost of installation and operation, full respect of privacy, 12-months or more of battery lifetime, wide variety of event detectable and easy to connect to existing or dedicated IT infrastructures.\nXETAL MoCa has been tested in nursing homes, office space and hospitals over a period of 18 months before the company official, and it has already started working on MoCa NextGen.','Reliable space monitoring without invading privacy','[\"Belgium\"]','Xetal'),('We are a management consultancy in Madeira, managing existing businesses as well as actively developing several new projects.\n\nExisting businesses:\n- www.naturemeetings.com - walking in Madeira and now developing a larger offer of outdoor activities in Madeira as well as stronger online presence and increasing distribution \n- www.quinta-das-colmeias.com - organic farming and holiday homes - increasing organic farm production and holiday let rentals sales\n- www.quintadofurao.com - 45 room hotel recently refurbished and improving EBITDA\n- www.themadeiraguide.com\n\nNew projects:\n- vermicomposting / composting\n- www.themadeiraguide.com - leading travel guide for Madeira\n- elder care village\n- 44 room 5 star boutique hotel and 33 flat development - possibility of golden visa application\n- acquire and recover centenary houses and maintain the asset through tourism holiday rentals','Madeira Business Consultancy','[\"Funchal\"]','ZINO'),('Mobile App:\nSafety and Rescue are easy effective ways to get help when something goes wrong. \nCaring reminders, check-ins, video and voice access to your home to manage kids, etc. \nManaged Groups offer access to safety & productivity services for the person responsible for a group.  \nCampus Safety is for detecting unusual or unwanted people or behavior on campus - detect, verify, respond, in seconds \nWrite-Once publishing sends to everyone you can address in any way, and publishes to key words','uCaring.com makes Doing the Right Thing easier.','[\"Carlsbad\"]','SafeTFirst Corportion'),('SeniorMove.com introduces Seniors and their Families to Seniors Real Estate Specialists® (SRES®) Realtors® who can help the Senior in whatever living transition they are embarking upon whether that be downsizing, moving across the country to be closer to family, or moving into a senior living community.','Real Estate Agent Lead Generation','[\"Denver\"]','SeniorMove.com'),(NULL,'4-Star Senior Living on Beautiful Lake Michigan','[]','The Whitcomb Senior Living Community'),('Build-up a near elderly house environment with a low monthly fee for senior people(55+) like to stay their lovely home rather than move to Continue Care Retired Community','Virtual Senior House','[\"Taipei\"]','55TONE International Corp.'),('Meetmeintime.com stores life stories in a time-capsule and releases it at the designated time to the designated recipient by fulfilling the wishes of the user.\nMotto:You will never be forgotten!\nProblems Addressed:\n1. What is the best way to preserve my legacy and life-story for the ones I care about and the world?\n2. How do I preserve the integrity of my name?\n3. How do I remind myself of my life once I grow old and possibly suffer from dementia?\nVoice recognition software allows users unprecedented ease of use. They only need to speak into the microphone and the site will automatically translate into words and stored. We provide Social networking platform.\nCustomer Base: seniors and baby-boomers.\n\n','lifestories in time capsule','[\"Dallas\"]','Meetmeintime'),('bacikalfa.com is helping both families and care providers by providing a place on internet for them to easily find each others.  Families can search for best possible care providers based on their own criteria such as location, education level, experience, care types —including  child care, tutoring, senior care, nursing, housekeeping, cooks, driver and more. As well as the service here enables care providers to find jobs based on their own criteria such as job type, location, salary and more.','Helping families and care providers to meet','[\"Istanbul\"]','BACIKALFA INSAN KAYNAKLARI'),('Omni is an iPhone / iPad app that allows you to create a timeline of your health. In just minutes, create a list of health problems, medications, procedures, surgeries, allergies, and more. Search instantly, store privately, and share with physicians of your choice. Omni makes medical records simple.\n','Medical record on your iPhone','[\"Oakland\"]','Omni Health Timeline'),('The most recent version of our unmanned aerial robots is an aerial rescue Semi-autonomous multi-rotor( nick-named Psitta after my CAG Parrot).\nOur innovative approach takes the rescue robotics operations to a higher level of physical and computational involvement. \nBasically the UAV not only observes the scene but also takes necessary action in case of disaster or life risk.\nThe platform is comprised of a flying robot, a multi-functional life saving payload(e.g inflatable life vest or ring), a ground control unit requiring minimal involvement( only high level decisions are made by the operators) and several accessories for mission fulfillment and drone maintenance.  \nCustomers from private and gov sector have already shown great interest and asked us for coop opportunities. Our marketing force is also being focused on the niche market of Super/Yacht owners and large resort managing firms.\nThe redundant modular design of Psitta enables it to be deployed in mission critical situations.\n',' aerial rescue robot','[\"Munich\"]','Caspian Robotics'),(NULL,'The personal trainer in your pocket.','[\"Boston\"]','RunKeeper'),('Platform to enable mobile personal training (iOS-only):\n\n- 10 trainer apps + one umbrella app live in App Store\n- Apps sell content (programs + HD multimedia) from real personal trainers (Avg. Sales Price = $8)\n- Trainers personalize & share workouts with individual clients, get data feedback\n- 8 trainer-partners from across fitness niches (from weightlifting to yoga, CrossFit to cardio)\n- Self-serve channel for long-tail trainers to publish workouts & sell content & equipment','Hybrid Personal Training','[\"San Francisco\"]','GAIN Fitness'),('Independently owned membership businesses such as fitness centers, dance studios, and continuing education classes struggle with managing the hundreds and thousands of members they interact with daily.  BizeeBee simplifies the relationship by making it easy to track status of memberships, process payments, and renew and retain members.\n\nBizeeBee keeps memberships up-to-date, and generates valuable analytics for the business regarding revenue, retention, and return on investment for promotions.\n','Memberships made easy.','[\"Palo Alto\"]','BizeeBee'),('GymPact is a mobile fitness startup that conquers excuses with $$$ as a motivator!\n\nMembers make a Pact of how many days a week they want to exercise, and how much they’ll put on the line to pay if they DON’T get to the gym.  If they meet their Pact by checking in at their gym with our iPhone app, they receive cash rewards, paid for by those who didn’t exercise.','Behavioral economics to motivate healthy goals','[\"San Francisco\"]','GymPact'),('Classtivity is a membership program for fitness classes across multiple gyms and studios, making working out more engaging and accessible. Since launching in early 2013, Classtivity has facilitated over 40,000 reservations at 1,000+ different classes in the New York market. \n','Good-bye Gym. Hello ClassPass ','[\"New York City\"]','Classtivity'),('Wello connects consumers with fitness professionals over LIVE, INTERACTI