software and smart-fabric enabled wearable devices for health and fitness. Heapsylon is focused on delivering a family of body-sensing devices. Our SDK proprietary sensor-enabled t-shirt, sport bra and smart-socks enable developers to build app that capture and communicate data such as activity type, heart rate, Gait and in-footwear pressure to the user. The data is presented and analyzed in an easy-to-use, mobile dashboard. Sensoria makes it more fun and safer to exercise by converting data in real-time actionable information. Over 30 million health and fitness devices were shipped in 2012, up 37% on 2011 (ABI). Sensor equipped wearable devices are projected to become a 400M unit market worth $4B by 2014 (Qualcomm/Dow Jones).','The Garment is the Computer.','[\"Redmond\"]','Heapsylon Sensoria Wearables'),('TRAINR is a personal trainer on your wrist – a consumer mobile software that integrates with any smart watch or fitness band to track anaerobic exercises (pushups, squats, curls, etc.). The app links with a wrist device\'s motion processing unit to identify the user\'s exercises and track reps, sets, and rest periods. TRAINR generates bespoke workouts and dynamic workout adjustments to create a personalized exercise experience.\n\nTRAINR is launching this month on the Samsung Galaxy Gear – however, the software is hardware-agnostic and will soon connect with any wrist-worn device. Next year, TRAINR will release sport-specific applications (swimming, yoga, tennis), sell enterprise packages to gyms and fitness professionals, and begin clearing regulatory hurdles for use in health care and physical therapy.','Evolving the wrist device: Auto tracking, training  & analysis for workouts','[\"Los Angeles\"]','TRAINR'),('We are reshaping pet parenting by bringing connected, mobile health to our furry family members. Our first product, FitBark, is a $99 wearable bone & mobile app that allows you to gain actionable insights into your dog\'s behavior and long term health trends. By understanding your dog better, you can take better care of her.','Be the best dog parent ever.','[\"New York City\"]','FitBark'),('Race Yourself is the world\'s first virtual reality fitness gaming platform for Google Glass.\n\nRace against a virtual avatar of yourself, against friends or celebrities, or flee from flesh eating zombies pursuing at your target pace. We aren\'t talking about audio feedback - we are talking about right on the road in front of you.\n\nOur goal is to improve one of the developed world\'s greatest health problems: lack of exercise. We are going to do this by bringing the gaming experience to exercise. All the perks of the exercise combined with the fun, addictive nature of gaming combined with the adrenaline of both.\n\nFor some this will be racing yourself, visualising improvement. For some this will mean competing with friends. For some this will be the gamified environment, earning points from burning calories and building streaks to unlock further features and rewards. For us it\'s going to be fleeing from a 500ft high Godzilla - but each to their own.','Virtual fitness motivation','[\"San Francisco\"]','Race Yourself'),('As an athlete, I learned that protein is critical for performance.  Protein is a secret gem of nutrients - the human body needs it constantly throughout the day.\n\nSpartos all-natural protein waters:\n\n10 grams Whey Protein Isolate\n9 Vitamin and Minerals\n4 Electrolytes\nFortified Antioxidants\n5,200mg Essential Amino Acids\nPrebiotics\nCane Sugar or Stevia sweetened (sugar free)\nCaffeine Free\nGluten and Soy Free\n\nBALANCE - RECOVER - FOCUS - PURIFY - HYDRATE - VITALIZE - REFRESH - STRENGTHEN - CLEANSE','Spartos: the First All-Natural Protein Water','[\"Los Angeles\"]','Spartan Beverages'),('Moves is a new way to understand how much physical exercise you get – just by keeping your phone in a pocket or bag. The app automatically recognizes activities (walking, running, cycling, transportation), routes and places. The data is visualized on a map and as a daily storyline that encourages you to take small steps towards more healthy habits and lifestyle. There is no need to start and stop the app as it runs continuously on the background.','Let your phone tell you how much you move','[\"Helsinki\"]','Moves'),('MyFitnessWallet is a complete health management and fitness analysis solution designed especially with the current health/fitness conscious generation in mind. \nThis multi faceted tool provides a simple and integrated platform for individuals with existing medical conditions and hospitals/clinics treating them, fitness enthusiasts as well as those who just want to keep a track of what they eat and do on a daily basis. \n','Monitor your health and fitness… the easy way','[\"Santiago\", \"Singapore\"]','MyFitnessWallet'),('BetterYou is an online marketplace where consumers can browse, buy and book directly with high-quality fitness and beauty professionals for less.  \n\nInstead of giving up 80% to a gym or a spa, BetterYou professionals are given a simple way to create online storefront in less than five minutes. They can manage their current clients and connect with new customers.\n\nConsumers buying on BetterYou save an average of 50% on services and can schedule their appointments in real time.\n\n','Amazon for Fitness and Beauty Services','[\"Los Angeles\"]','BetterYou '),('Our SaaS platform enables any organization to create and deliver anywhere, anytime telehealth, telelearning or teletraining programs and services. \n\nNow, care providers; schools; sports/fitness training academies/franchises; & corporate training departments can extend video-based progressive workflows; coordinate & track their members with automated programs; provide personalized two-way feedback on uploaded videos; and broadcast media to drive revenue, reduce costs or be more efficient.','Enabling organizations to deliver anywhere, anytime telecare, telelearning or teletraining','[\"Washington, DC\"]','ViiNetwork'),('We have designed and built an electronically-controlled automatic shifting system that greatly enhances the bike-riding experience for the casual and recreational rider.  We currently feature this system on our own line of cruiser/comfort bikes and we are also partnering with OEMs who will feature our shifting system on some of their product lines.','Evolving the bicycle','[\"Detroit\"]','AutoBike'),('SportID is an online health and sport benefit service for companies who want to motivate their employees and reduce overhead in healthcare costs. The company gets all services with 1 invoice per month. Our active team helps them to achieve the goal of getting healthy, happy and more productive employees. Sport works!\n\nHow it works? Company joins with SportID, uploads employee data and sets the health budget. Employees get instant access to a wide range of wellness service providers and special corporate pricing at sport clubs. By using SportID, employees can use their sport credit as they like! ','Tool for companies to create easy employee wellness management system','[\"Tartu\"]','SportID'),('Hyperwear is a leading innovative consumer products brand in functional fitness and wellness: a market which has grown 11% annually from 2007-2012. The free weight market is vast but has not seen any innovation in decades. Current products include the Hyper Vest weight vests, and the SandBell and SteelBell free weights that do what medicine balls, kettlebells and dumbbells can do and much, much more. More patent pending products are launching in 2013, including a cooling vest to activate brown adipose tissue which burns calories for weight loss. Hyperwear is building service and media sales with workout DVDs, group exercise programming, and education. Fitness First in the UK, one of the world\'s premier clubs, has started to offer Hyperwear\'s SandBell group exercise programming and SATS, a 100 club Nordic chain should follow. A strategic marketing study is underway testing a 20 minute home workout program for women. \nComing to: Every health club, Every weight room, and Every home.','Functional fitness and wellness consumer brand with disruptive products high growth market','[\"Austin\"]','Hyperwear® '),('Today\'s society is sedentary and addicted to virtual worlds. Epidemic levels of health related complications include obesity, diabetes and reduced lifespans. In addition, face-to-face relationships are becoming a thing of the past. \n\nAt Physical Apps we take Real-world Experiences and Supercharge them with Smart Devices. We take traditional and wholesome activities like face-to-face play, learning, tabletop games and exercise, and supercharge them with music, video, voice and more. TheO SmartBall Jr, our first product, is an award winning smartphone enabled ball that promotes activities that are as compelling as today\'s virtual experiences. Our propriety products keep people and devices safe. Line extensions include SmartDisk, SmartAerobics and SmartWeight.','Wii-like experiences using mobile','[\"Boston\"]','Physical Apps'),('teamup is a payment and registration system for small to mid-sized fitness studios.  We provide a full featured, lightly branded widget that businesses can place on their website to allow customers to register for classes and events.  We support recurring monthly membership payments and discount codes, process USD and GBP, and offer reporting tools designed specifically for fitness businesses.','straightforward scheduling and payments for the sports and fitness industry','[\"Silicon Valley\"]','teamup'),('Vint is a marketplace for personal trainers in any sport and all skill levels. Training for a marathon? Want to try out rock climbing? Just trying to get moving? We\'ve got you covered.\r\n\r\nOur app makes it easy to find suitable activities near you. Talk to the instructor, book, and pay for the activity in the app. It\'s as simple as that.\r\n\r\nEvery instructor is approved by us at Vint. Not all are certified professionals, but all of them are highly skilled athletes with a passion for teaching other people. We do our very best to find a broad variety of instructors, and we highly value the quality of their work.\r\n\r\nYou can browse their upcoming activities through our app and, once you find something you like, make a reservation right away. No member fees or year-long subscriptions, just personal training on your terms.','Vint is a marketplace for personal trainers in any sport','[\"Stockholm\"]','Vint'),('Our algorithms for successfully creating and maintaining a relationship with a patient power our long-term behavior change platform.  The first product built on top of this platform is our Autom™ weight loss coach.\n\nAutom™ is like having a personal coach at home and is shown to be more effective than other behavior change programs for motivating a person over time.\n\nBuilt on years of research at the MIT Media Lab and Boston University Med Center, first customers include health insurers, hospitals, big pharma, employers, and individuals.','Interactive long-term behavior change','[\"Hong Kong\"]','Intuitive Automata'),('Recently dubbed \"Spotify of Fitness\" by Top European financial publication.\n\nWe match consumers to locally relevant fitness activities, facilities, and services based on interests and profile using proprietary technology.\n\nFor wellness service providers, we create value by obtaining exclusive free trials and repackaging them as a discovery tool to create pre-qualified leads. Further we provide an effective platform for affiliate sales for our providers.\n\nCurrently live and based out of NYC & Finland. Contact us for further information.','Experience fitness products and services you\'ll love','[\"New York City\"]','SportSetter'),('Training Mobs lets you easily find and share awesome group workouts near you. You can also add your own, and invite friends and others from the community to join you.\n\nOur \"Mobsters\" love it because it\'s clean, simple and helps them find just 2 things: awesome workouts, and committed people to do them with.\n\nTrainers, Studios and Gym owners use our site to post workouts, and more effectively reach their target market.','Website and social fitness community that helps you find awesome group workouts near you.','[\"Montreal\"]','Training Mobs'),('upmysport helps you connect with recommended sport & fitness instructors and book their activities online. \n\nWe\'re passionate about sport & fitness. About its benefits, and the positive impact instructors have. By better connecting people with instructors, we can boost participation, and help more instructors earn a good living. \n\nupmysport takes people on their entire sporting journey: personal training, weekly yoga classes, private tennis lessons, yearly ski courses, one-off trekking trips... All activities. In one place. For the first time.\n\nAnd we\'re uniting the community of instructors with a common passion: to help people reach their potential. By supporting instructors with better marketing, an online reputation and a simple way to manage bookings & payments, we\'re building a trusted marketplace in a $40bn+ worldwide market, where they help us grow, and everyone succeeds. ','The marketplace for guided sport & fitness activities','[\"London\"]','upmysport'),('NeuVerus understands that sustained behavior change for individuals and corporate wellness requires a fresh approach.  We have developed a formula that combines entertaining content and game play with intrinsic motivation.\n\nNeuFit, our social fitness game, encourages everyone to get and stay active. Our technology platform feeds players real-world daily activity from devices into compelling, high quality game environments, encouraging players to compete, challenge, and adopt healthy behaviors.','Entertain - Engage - Sustain','[\"San Francisco\"]','NeuVerus Health'),('Learn all about us at: http://igg.me/at/skulpt\n\nThe Skulpt Aim lets you measure the fat percentage and muscle quality (MQ) for individual muscles and your whole body. Data is transferred wirelessly to an online dashboard where you can track your progress and get exercise advice. Smaller than an iPhone, the glossy, portable Aim was designed to fit comfortably in your palm as it hugs your muscles. It’s strong and waterproof. Use it anywhere, any time. \n\nAim’s design has already made Skulpt an International CES Innovations 2014 Design and Engineering Awards Honoree.','Measure your muscle fitness','[\"Miami\"]','Skulpt'),('FitDeck is a unique deck of playing cards that makes exercise and sports training more simple, convenient, and fun. FitDeck, Inc. has sold nearly 500,000 units to customers and organizations in 130 countries, generating over $4.3 million in revenue. We have built a content library that consists of 40 different FitDeck “titles” with unique workouts targeted to different market segments (e.g. adults, children, coaches, athletes) and fitness programs (e.g. CrossFit, Suspension Training). \n\nFitDeck has gone digital, productizing our unique formula that makes any exercise format more simple, convenient, and fun across all mobile platforms. We are now raising our first outside capital to build out our technology team, expand our network of FitDeck applications across all mobile platforms, and begin to build out the FitDeck platform into the global leader in digital fitness and training for both consumers and fitness professionals. \n','Digital Exercise Playing Cards','[\"San Diego\"]','FitDeck'),('Mobile app to help consumers avoid long lines and crowded venues by providing realtime & forecasted crowdedness data. Our first vertical is gyms, and future verticals include restaurants/cafes, bars/clubs, theme parks, and more.','Realtime traffic for gyms and other venues: Waze for venues.','[\"Los Angeles\"]','GymFlow'),('Cody is a fitness community for sharing and discovering workouts. \n\nTrack your progress and get support from an encouraging community. \n\nFind new workouts by following trainers and people like you. ','A supportive fitness community for sharing and discovering workouts.','[\"Seattle\"]','Cody'),('FitCause is a social fundraising platform empowering individuals to turn everyday motion into a charitable donation. We make it simple for users to fundraise for causes by leveraging fitness data from activity trackers. We also work with corporations to develop and sponsor group missions that set goals of fitness data, and link it to corporate donations. \n\nWith FitCause, everyone now has the ability to do well for themselves and do well for the world at the same time','Get Fit. Give Back. Change Lives.','[\"New York City\"]','FitCause'),('Strength in numbers. \n\nPUSH is an app-enabled fitness device that tracks and analyzes your strength performance at the gym. \n\nOur team has worked tirelessly for the last year to bring the fitness realm a new wearable device that generates real metrics. No imaginary points or arbitrary scores, just actual data that will help make you stronger, improve your form and reduce the risk of injury. ','Cutting-edge training tech for the elite athlete.','[\"Toronto\"]','PUSH'),('The world needs a new brand of what it means to be fit. Exercise shouldn\'t be a chore, it should be entertainment. \n\nPart technology, part media company LiveExercise is a Next Gen Health & Fitness Media Network. We achieve this with engaging \"Live Reality\" Content powered by Intelligent Data all wrapped in the Social Web. \n\nWe take exercising at home, personalize it and make it social; tracking individual user behavior to create custom workout programs, while providing access to personal trainers and a community of workout partners. We are family focused, with shows for everyone from kids to grandma. Unlike other fitness programs we don\'t offer \"30 Day promises\", instead we offer \"exercise as entertainment\" creating a long-term relationship with our users. Our Live format is unlike anything else - with over 30 hours of new content every-week. This keeps the overall experience fresh, enabling us to adapt quickly to user feedback and keep our retention rates high.  ','Exercise as Entertainment','[\"Boca Raton\"]','LiveExercise'),('Dittit is a platform for personal goal achievement.\n\nWith us, you either achieve social glory or suffer the consequences! Our community of users attain their lifelong ambitions by publicly stating their goals and reinforcing their commitments with financial rewards, penalties and social peer pressure.\n\nDittit - you’re gonna make it. (Because if you don’t, we’re gonna charge you money and tell all your friends)','Goal Achievement, Accountability, Motivation ','[\"Silicon Valley\"]','Dittit'),('There are tons of knowledgeable fitness trainers out there, but very few know how to create a high-quality online service that leverages that knowledge.\r\n\r\nHaving underwent a major pivot a year ago, we have decided to open WorkoutBOX up at a platform for all qualified trainers to create their own online interactive fitness company - complete with a mobile app, tech support, continuous development, etc - for no cost up front. \r\n\r\nUsing our custom-built step-by-step program creation wizard, trainers can create their own unique landing page and interactive day-by-day fitness plan complete with customized meal planning - all for free (we take 30% of subscriptions).\r\n\r\nNot only are we a platform for fitness program creation, but we\'re also a discovery engine and ratings system for trainers. Think Udemy for fitness.\r\n\r\nWe already get approx 300k uniques/month from free organic search, and were ranked as one of the top 5 online fitness services in the world in 2011 and 2012.','Udemy-like Platform for Personal Trainers','[\"Los Angeles\"]','WorkoutBOX'),('ScienceBehindSweat helps athletes and coaches get accurate individualized analysis of training and biometric data. We close the information loop and help athletes improve performance by fixing inefficiencies and skill deficits in a data driven manner. Founded by PhD geneticists and statisticians who are collegiate athletes, RxAnalytics combines in-depth domain expertise with proprietary machine learning creating a novel platform for behavior, health metrics and performance analysis and personalized recommendations. We are focused on CrossFit to start and will be moving into collegiate team sports next.','Big data driven personalized fitness roadmaps','[\"Durham\"]','RxAnalytics'),('Skinnyo lets ordinary people start or join challenges that make it a little easier to stay healthy. They can compete with friends and colleagues to lose weight in custom health challenges that take minutes to setup.','Health and Fitness Challenges','[\"United Kingdom\"]','Skinnyo'),('Gymdeck\'s mobile applications help fitness professionals and independent contractors stay on top of things and earn more money. Billing, scheduling and client management, all under one roof, on the go.\n\nTechCrunch Europe write-up at launch:\n\nhttp://eu.techcrunch.com/2011/03/22/gymdeck-is-a-new-mobile-app-aimed-at-disorganised-personal-trainers/','Mobile applications that help fitness professionals stay on top of things','[\"London\"]','Gymdeck'),(NULL,'A Digital Platform for Health and Fitness Brands','[\"Mountain View\"]','Exercise.com'),('GymRealm\'s manager (www.gymrealm.com/manager) is a cloud based service, delivering innovative business management software to club owners in the health and wellness industry worldwide. ','B2B SaaS for Sport Centers','[\"Sofia\"]','GymRealm '),('PumpUp is a mobile fitness coaching platform that combines personalization, guidance, and community to help you live a healthy and active lifestyle. It’s the best way to get active, stay motivated, and see great results.\n\nWe have strong traction, we\'re growing rapidly, and our users love PumpUp.\n\nPrimary contact: phil@pumpup.co','Personalized Fitness Coaching Platform','[\"Waterloo\"]','PumpUp'),('ChampionVillage is an online fitness community for kids. Create your own profile in minutes and start earning rewards for making healthy decisions. Link up with your friends and classmates. Engage in friendly competition and build out your own personal tree house. Being healthy has never been so fun or easy!','Online fitness platform for kids','[\"Provo\"]','ChampionVillage'),('Each year, runners spend $1.5 billion (growing 11.5% annually) to race. Yog gives them access to this same experience every time they lace up their shoes.\n\nRunning is great for its simplicity, but it becomes boring without the social support and competition of running partners. \n\nWe\'ve developed a way for the millions of runners around the world who run everyday to compete in real-time, without the cognitive overhead of coordinating meeting locations and start times.\n\nOver time, our proprietary algorithm learns about your performance and habits to connect with you the ideal running partners to push your performance.\n\n\n','Your daily run, now a global race.','[\"San Francisco\"]','Yog'),('VirtualU\'s product, VFit, is a 3D human scanner designed for the health and fitness. The VFit experience allows users to track versions of their body over time, seeing up to 2mm changes in their body. VFit also provides key numerical data on the health of your body through measurements such as BMI, Fat %, Height, Weight, Heart Rate, and more.','3D Human Avatar Platform','[\"Blacksburg\"]','VirtualU'),('Electrozyme is engaged in the development of its patented technology, printed electrochemical sensors capable of transducing relevant metabolic information from the epidermis of the wearer in a non-invasive, non-obtrusive, and cost-effective fashion. The Company has already demonstrated working prototypes and has priority access to a state-of-the-art printing facility to begin pilot production in conjunction with a strategic partner(s), who will provide co-development revenue.','Epidermal biosensors for fitness assessment','[\"San Diego\"]','Electrozyme'),('My FitOption is a mobile application that is like the GPS for weight management and fitness, that help people on the go reach their health fitness goals. My FitOption is an accelerator to any diet or fitness program to ensure the users success.There are a 108 million Americans who actively try to lose weight every year and they spend $66.5 billion a year to do so. There are many fads in the health and fitness industry and we want to take advantage of this ever growing market. Our application is a life management tool that remind people when to eat, when to workout and give specific suggestions based on users personal goals.  ','GPS for weight management and fitness','[\"Denver\"]','My FitOption Inc.'),('Fitgame helps people stay engaged with weightloss. ','Visual tracking and game mechanics for fitness','[\"Boulder\"]','Fitgame'),('Worldwide\'s fitness group class search and book engine. No membership required!\n\nAn Internet platform where people can find and book virtually any fitness class they want to book online.\n\nFitboo is a search engine, fully integrated with the back-end booking across thousands of fitness providers, where you can book fitness group classes in gyms based on multiple locations at your convenience. Gym membership is a great option for people who can attend on a regular basis, but not everyone falls into that category.\n\nfitboo is a free tool for gym owners seeking to market their businesses, attract new customers and fill empty seats.','Airbnb for fitness clubs. Pay as you go for customers.','[\"New York City\"]','fitboo'),('Rock My World is creating the next evolution of how hundreds of millions of people experience music during physical activities.\n\nDuring fitness activities, our technology takes in data from sensors in smartphones and wearable devices.  We leverage this data to, in real-time, change music tempo to best help someone reach their fitness goals.\n\nRock My World’s proof-of-concept application, RockMyRun:\n• Is the #1 app for running music\n• 100k+ registered users\n• Launched as #3 paid Health & Fitness app & top 100 overall paid app (iOS)\n• 100% DMCA compliant\n\nBy leveraging data from the exploding wearable devices market and ultimately embedding our core technology in other devices, we\'ll capitalize on the growing $45B health & fitness market.','Leveraging Wearables To Adapt Music in Real-time','[\"San Diego\"]','Rock My World'),('PlayFitness allows users from any country to choose fitness experts who may live thousands miles away. Users and trainers can interact with each other in real time via internet video conferencing in a comfort of their own homes. PlayFitness frees users from any additional devices and offers a privacy feature. A user has a choice to be seen by a trainer as a live person or can switch to an avatar mode with help of Microsoft Kinect technology and be visible to a trainer as an avatar character. \n','Interactive Fitness and Wellness Portal','[\"New York City\"]','PlayFitness'),('Jamo brings the Just Dance game, the best-selling third-party game on Wii, to mobile phones by turning your phone into a Wii console and Wii controller. Jamo\'s MotionMatch technology can objectively score how well a user has followed the instructor, thus turning any dance or dance fitness routine into a game. \n\nJamo is not just a clone of the Just Dance game, it is also a mobile platform for Dancers and Dance Fitness instructors. The Jamo App completely automates motion capturing, so that any instructor can publish new routines easily. They can list a new routine for a fee, and Jamo helps them monetize their dance talent.\n\nConsumers of the Jamo App benefit from the large repository of instructors and routines, so that their workout is never boring again. Social interactions (challenges, group goals) across location and time help user stay engaged.\n','Just Dance on mobile + Instagram','[\"Sunnyvale\"]','Jamo'),('Find Your Trainer (FYT) is an online platform that will revolutionize the $9B personal training industry in a similar way OpenTable, ZocDoc and Uber have revolutionized dining, doctors, and car services. FYT works with leading fitness clubs to sell their ~$10B in excess training inventory by removing all of the friction related to getting a personal trainer. \n\nFind Your Trainer creates a win-win-win for users, trainers and gyms. Anyone interested in personal training can research trainers and book affordable sessions in just 3 clicks without having to talk to a sales person, while trainers are able to increase their income by filling their downtime with new clients. Gyms have the most to gain by being on Find Your Trainer --  incremental training sessions generate completely incremental profit, improve member satisfaction and reduce member churn. And by allowing non-members to train at their facilities, Find Your Trainer is a great source for highly-qualified, paid lead generation.\n  ','ZocDoc for personal training','[\"New York City\"]','Find Your Trainer (FYT)'),('We have developed THE mobile app that lets amateur athletes be coached through workouts by their favorite professional athletes. Coachd is more than just a new way to elevate your game, its the ONLY way you can train, play and be, like the pros. ','Train, play and be like the pros. ','[\"Waterloo\"]','Coachd'),('SpotMe automates gym reimbursement benefits.','Attendance Based Gym Reimbursements','[\"New York City\"]','SpotMe'),('TWID is a web-based Social CRM tool for fitness clubs. Clubs need to capture new members and prevent them from terminating their memberships. Customer acquisition and retention is increasingly expensive, and clubs have difficulties up selling to current members. \nTWID provides all the functionality and modules a fitness club needs to i) attract more members, ii) increase current member stickiness (through engagement) and iii) extract more money from their members through up selling.\n','Social CRM software for fitness clubs','[\"Helsinki\"]','Twid'),('KLUTCHclub is a subscription-based service allowing consumers to try new health and wellness products by receiving a monthly package in the mail.  \n\nOrganized around a monthly theme, products include healthy snack foods, fitness gear and workout tips, as well as skincare regimens.  \n\nMembership includes exclusive promotions, expert content (e.g., celebrity fitness tips), and access to an interactive, user driven online community (e.g., product reviews).','Monthly subscription of health, wellness, and fitness products','[\"Chicago\"]','KLUTCHclub'),('BodBot tailors workout regimens according to your goals, abilities, schedule, equipment, and much more. As you exercise, BodBot learns, adjusts and improves with your results.\n\nThe product of years of work, Bodbot’s algorithm spans across physiology, biomechanics, neuroscience and related fields. BodBot is accessible on the web, iPhone and Android, and our users absolutely love us:\n\n\"THANK YOU THANK YOU THANK YOU for creating this.\" - Ryan\n\"This is a godsend.\" - Brian L \n\"Genius.\" - D Harris \n','Online personal trainer, strength coach, and performance specialist.','[\"San Francisco\"]','BodBot'),('StrengthPortal is a fitness management software for personal trainers that will increase the revenue of their business and save them time. The current systems that are used to track progress for clients (excel, pen & paper) are outdated and time-consuming. Our software will allow trainers to track every rep, personal record, and session completed by their clients throughout their workout programs. This information will then be compiled into organized and meaningful metrics for both the trainer and client to use to track progress. ','Fitness Management Software for Personal Trainers','[\"Silicon Valley\"]','StrengthPortal'),('From the moment your child complains of a fever, or starts coughing – a clock has begun. Sickness has a progression of events. Symptoms are clues as to what is wrong.\n\nIt’s usually nothing. A cold. A bad shrimp. A red swelling. Sometimes it’s not. And being able to tell the difference as quickly as possible is imperative.\n\nYou can’t run to a doctor every time someone sniffles. But you can accurately track what any doctor would request– a first responder’s accurate chronology of events.\n','\"The Mint.com of Personal Medical Data\"','[\"San Francisco\"]','MedChart'),('Our app helps users attain the lifestyle they visualised when they first signed up for their gym membership.','Gym habit app to change your lifestyle','[\"Melbourne\"]','LifeGym'),('We are a web-based payment system helping health & fitness professionals simplify transactions with clients using fast, flexible payments.\n\nWe enable health, fitness and wellness professionals to offer customisable packages and membership plans to their customers. With easy setup for one-off or recurring payments, we help reduce late cancellations and no shows turning casual visitors into recurring clients with on time payments. We take the pain out of the transaction with a simple and social experience whilst managing online payments.\n\n\n','BigCommerce for service providers','[\"Sydney\"]','MemberPass'),('StreamFIT (SF) is a subscription-based service providing streaming fitness videos available anytime, anywhere on any device with internet access. SF offers both free and paid membership options. Paid options include \"Unlimited Monthly\" which provides an unlimited amount of streaming workout videos for only $19.99/month and \"Unlimited Annual\" which provides a one-year paid-in-full price of $120 for unlimited access. Free membership provides limited access to four pre-selected videos each month that are ad-supported.','The fitness version of Netflix','[\"Milwaukee\"]','StreamFIT'),('Healthify My Team offers on site fitness and health based events to small and mid-sized companies through a managed services online platform. Our core offering will be focused around providing on site weekly fitness events and services to our customers. Companies are signed on through a consultative process, starting with a detailed needs assessment where we study the size and needs of their workforce. After this assessment, we will make basic recommendations and sign customers up for a monthly subscription of our services. Our services will include but are not be limited to any type of instructor led fitness class, from yoga to boxing, etc. We will also create employee led groups such as running clubs, and walking groups where we coach an employee on how to effectively lead a team in a healthy activity. By offering a wide range of services, we are seeking to engage employees of all fitness levels, abilities and comfort. ','In office fitness providers for small companies','[\"Chicago\"]','Healthify My Team'),('With our web connected 3D body scanners, our users have a unique ability to see their bodies change as they take part in a fitness or nutrition program.  We all like to see the results of our hard work and those entering into healthier lifestyles are no different.  By taking a part in the Fit3D program, users track nutrition and activity daily and take scans each week.  They are then able to act with our web platform to see how their body is changing as a result of their healthier lifestyles.  We offer interactive tools that continue to engage with each interaction.\n\nWe know how hard it is to stick to a healthy and active regime, so we build the tools that help you \"Visualize a healthier you.\" ','Next Generation Fitness Assessment Platform','[\"San Francisco\"]','Fit3D'),('Fitsby is a free mobile app that groups users into fitness buddies to create a meaningful experience that a user grows from and keeps coming back to . \n\nFitsby\'s technology is driven by big data. Which is used to group users into worthwhile group ecosystems and employ effective behavioral change techniques. \n\n','An app that motivates you to work out.','[\"Champaign\"]','Fitsby'),('Tracking your progress and other CrossFit achievements can be cumbersome. Gone are the days of plain, ugly looking WOD trackers and notepads.\n\nEnter WODcast -- a simple app for affiliates and members to track WOD performance.','Simple CrossFit WOD Tracker','[\"Hoboken\"]','WODcast'),('Anyone can use Routino (http://routino.com) to find good workout routines.','Spotify for your body','[\"Boston\"]','BTBK'),('Trainsweet is a SaaS platform for sports & fitness paired with our own social network. Built to be easy for all users, yet powerful enough for elite coaches. \n\nThe software allows people to plan, build and share customized training programs, and monitor their athletes\' progress.  It\'s being utilized by coaches, personal trainers and physical therapists.\n\nAthletes are able to log their workouts, connect with their coaches, teammates, and training buddies.  And monitor their progress over time.','SaaS platform for sports/fitness paired with our own social network.','[\"Silicon Valley\", \"San Francisco\"]','Trainsweet Labs'),('Activore enables health clubs and fitness professionals to address their most expensive problem -- member/client retention -- by engaging them through a gamified, venue-based social intranet platform and identifying with a motivational lifestyle brand. Each private network hosts an array of features for staff and members, including communication and scheduling tools.\n\nThe Activore platform is cloud-based Software as a Service for developing connections between real people belonging to a real-world group or venue. Our model is B2B with a strong consumer-driven brand, which will enable us to derive revenue through multiple streams, with the initial focus being SaaS subscriptions for health clubs and group fitness programs, and later opportunities including market insight metrics, ad sales, and merchandise.\n','Member engagement and social networking platform for fitness venues','[\"New York City\"]','Activore'),('Trulee is a social platform that caters to the fitness individual (Trainers,Coaches and Athletes). Trulee takes data from \"Body Devices\" in this case the Nike Fuel Bands, analyzes the data behavior patters to target messages to improve daily routines (nutrition,workouts,hydration,wellness), provide positive motivation,enforce accountability and sell services and products.\n\nWhen you wake up in the morning... Trulee is waiting on your phone...\n\n\"Good morning Troy, I see today is your running day, here is your running information from last week\"\n\nI get up and go for a run... and come home... weight myself with a Fitbit scale... and synch my Nike watch data...\n\n\"I see your time was better by 20 seconds, GREAT JOB! and your down 3 pounds this week..., Its time for your monthly blood pressure checkup.\"\n\nI use my Withing Pressure device...\n\n\"Your pressure is looking much better\"\n\nThis may sound like science fiction, but we have figured out how to do this and much more today!!!\n\n\n\n','It\'s Google Analytics for fitness!','[\"Pleasanton\"]','Trulee'),('FitCampus is a site for college students to track their workouts, compete with friends and win rewards from healthy brands.','Connecting active brands to active students.','[\"Boston\"]','FitCampus'),('At Cycle My City we have built a cycling activity tracker for cyclists who prefer to ride socially. To this end we are incorporating features to connect cyclists to others, help cyclists find group rides and evaluate their ability to join each group ride. We\'ll be adding team cycling functions and a whole lot of unique features that we expect will disrupt activity tracking websites in general, which we would be happy to confidentially discuss with potential investors in more detail separately.\nFurther, we are creating local hubs around existing bike stores with novel implentations of existing technology that will lead to first revenue quickly.','Local Cycling Networks, Globally','[\"Perth\"]','Cycle My City'),('Campus Protein provides college students with affordable brand-name vitamins & supplements with free same-day delivery through our online website. Campus Protein has distribution centers stationed at different colleges across the nation, run by students. On the website there is an option at checkout for “Free Same-Day Delivery”. After the customer completes their order a text message is sent to set up a convenient delivery time. One of our drivers delivers the order the same day free of charge.\n','Discounted Supplements & Convenient Delivery for College Students','[\"United States\"]','CampusProtein.com'),('MVF is a highly-efficient fitness and nutrition program. Our core 16-week program (mandatory for all new members) focuses on creating beneficial habits that make long-term fitness goals sustainable, achievable, and measurable.\n\nThe program includes one-on-one coaching, educational programming, and a customized nutrition/exercise plan, with a supportive, online community of other members who are also going through the program. We also take in all of the quantified self data our members choose to provide us to assist in our coaching, organized on a single dashboard.','Fitness for Tech Entrepreneurs (and other busy people)','[\"New York City\"]','Minimum Viable Fitness'),('SFM provides online class and appointment management, customer accounts and profiles, web templates and customization, mobile and social media presence ect. Think Shopify.com, for the 25,000 independent small businesses, currently running on ICal and Quickbooks. What EBay did for the guy selling vintage collectables, we do for personal trainers, tutors, yoga instructors, independent lawyers, hairdressers, therapists, shake charmers, and the rest of the $50B independent service industry. \n\n\n\n\n','What EBay did for garage sales, we do for the independent and self employed. ','[\"San Franci