ication)','[\"Atlanta\"]','cMEcompete'),('Train with top sports & fitness coaches over 2-way, streaming video. Using a webcam + wifi, athletes everywhere can train with the country\'s top experts in sports, fitness and personal health anytime, anywhere and at a much lower cost than ever before. ','Live coaching with one click.','[\"San Francisco\"]','Fitzeal'),('Oxirate delivers continuous mobile vital sign monitoring and reporting enabled by a proprietary low power sensing platform.\nOxirate transmits raw PPG (Photoplethysmography) and inertial data from the earlobe sensor to a smart phone or a server for processing. Complete data log and results of data processing are available for “cloud” based apps. Oxirate’s sensing platform uses innovative reflective pulse oximetry, advanced signal processing, and low power wireless technology\n','Mobile low power vital sign monitor','[\"Sunnyvale\"]','Oxirate'),('The opportunity: take the world’s greatest glanceable display – the watch - and reinvent it as a stylish and simple, glanceable display for when we are really mobile and on the go. Glance is a powerful interface for mobile internet services.\n\nMeta Watch helps consumers do what they are already trying to do - consume mobile alerts & notifications effortlessly. This has become a big problem because alerts are often missed because of we carry our phones (guys in pocket; ladies in handbag). \n','Smart watches that function as a glanceable display for critical alerts & the mobile web','[\"Dallas\"]','Meta Watch'),('Funl is a tool for building a better you.\n\nThe mechanism is simple: create habits that you want to add to your life, and reward yourself each time you perform them. Using Funl, you pay yourself to build the life you want!\n\nEach Habit in Funl has a small financial incentive attached. As you perform these Habits, a payout will be directed into the Reward of your choosing, helping you progress toward your goal.','Build good habits by linking your activities 