ivitamin, SUPERLUX, that started with 2000IU of vitamin D3 per serving.  This is the most vitamin D3 available in a multivitamin but it is the amount that doctors are frequently recommending to their patients.  We built the complete formula from the ground up using modern diets and the latest in scientific research as our guide.  We included only the best forms of each ingredient, (Mixed carotenoids for vitamin A, tocotrienols for vitamin E, etc) at the optimal dosage.  Other multivitamin formulas have not changed their formulas since the late 1960\'s when the Daily Values were established.\n\nBuilding on our multivitamin, we have created a system of products that will complement each other in a simple to understand manner removing the complexity currently in the buying process for consumers. ','Vitamin D Focused Premium Nutritional Supplements','[\"Detroit\"]','SunDaily'),('Our service is an integrated tracking and sensor platform to enable sport professionals to track, analyze and improve their performance.The platform is made of a unique smartphone accessory, a smartphone application and an Internet service. For more info, check our website: http://www.selfloops.com','you can improve only what you measure','[\"Fermo\"]','selfloops'),('Optimized Training Labs is a completely new way to look at endurance training for triathletes and runners. It harnesses the knowledge of coaches, scientific study, and complex mathematics to generate a completely customized training plan to help you reach your goals while allowing schedule flexibility for everyday life.','Optimized for Smarter Triathlon and Running Training','[\"Dallas\"]','Optimized Training Labs'),('Share It Fitness acts as both a B2C fitness instruction provider and a B2B subscription platform connecting Fitness Providers with Consumers via a white-labeled video blogging platform.  For a monthly cost less than ONE in-person training session.  \n\nWe are building Share It Fitness to provide consumers a medium that