vent chronic diseases. At the same time main stream and complementary medical providers do not have reliable and affordable way to engage and monitor their patients/clients outside of their practice. \n\nTracking, managing, and optimizing wellness without major administrative component. Total HealthScore will be a proven way that optimizes engagement. \n\nFrom the medical provider point of view, THCard lowers customer acquisition costs by providing a large group of healthcare consumers and a commission-only payment platform. \n \n ','Mint.com For Health And Fitness','[\"Denver\"]','Total Health Card'),('IREHAB builds web and mobile applications for Physical Therapy and Fitness.  Our products provide better accessible and cost effective care for professionals, patients, consumers, hospitals, universities and insurance companies. \n\nTools for professionals to better serve their patients and customers.  And applications for consumers to get Physical Therapy care anytime anywhere and without needing an office visit.','Physical Therapy and Fitness apps for web and mobile','[\"Hawaii\"]','IREHAB.com'),('Healbe is the simple way to manage your body weight, health and sport results, whoever you are.\n\nWristband on your hand fully automatically \n- calculates how much calories earned with the foods and spent duting any activity\n- trackes your heart rate, pulse wave, blood pressure, respiratory rate, temperature, sleep phase, level of dehydration and stress. \n\nApp on your mobile device synchronizes with wristband via bluetooth and gives you understanding, what happens with your body','Automatically trackes your body weight, health and sport results','[\"Moscow\"]','Healbe'),('FitChimp is redefining the fitness culture in the work place by enabling employees to get in quick 2-5 minute workouts at work, without requiring change of clothes or showering. \n\nFitChimp Micro Fitness Solution is highly convenient and cost-effective when compared to gym memberships, on site group classes and even conventional on site gyms.\n\nBoost employee health, happiness and productivity!  \n','Micro Fitness Solution','[\"Austin\"]','FitChimp'),('FitPush is the ultimate app for fitness and healthy living. \n\nAccess thousands of FREE and premium fitness and nutrition programs prepared by professionals, track and analyze your progress, find people that inspire you and inspire others to stay on track for healthier lifestyle.\n\nAvailable this summer on iOS, Android and PC (through your favorite browser)\n\nIf you are fitness, sport or food / nutrition professional, we would like to hear from you at hello@fitpush.com\n\nFollow @fitpush on twitter!','App for fitness and nutrition','[\"Athens\"]','FitPush'),('How do we change our 98% stress, junk-food craving, inactive lifestyle?  \n\n21 million people in the US alone think that\'s it\'s by hiring a personal trainer.\n\nThey spend $9B a year to access a PT\'s energy, experience and accountability.  \n\nPersonal trainers are super motivating for the 2 hours a week we\'re with them but how do we stay on track when we\'re not with our trainer... like the other 99% of the time?\n\n--------\n\nTop Trainer finally makes remote personal accountability -  accessible, affordable and awesome. \n\n** Our software for personal trainers to slashes the time it takes to support clients remotely so trainers can reach more clients, make more money and change more lives. **\n\nTop Trainer is a B2B business so we can make money from day one but the future of Top Trainer is so much bigger and make a real difference on the 55% of us that struggle with our weight.\n\nWant to join us on a journey to transform health and fitness support forever?','Sparking the new age of health and fitness support','[\"Auckland\"]','Top Trainer'),('All Season makes expert athletic instruction free and accessible to everyone. Our website helps athletes and coaches learn and improve with engaging, short-video courses. All Season makes it easy to learn a new position, concept, or weightlifting technique among many subjects.\r\n','Free sports instruction courses','[\"Des Moines\"]','All Season'),('CrossFit is a rapidly growing sport and we\'ve created a way to bring all the athletes together, every day. WODstack is a workout tracking application specifically designed for CrossFitters. Our users come from all over the globe and we are growing rapidly. ','Workout Tracking for CrossFitters','[\"Dallas\"]','WODstack'),('PlayEnable is a two-sided marketplace for sports and fitness activities.\n\nPlayEnable’s aim is to enable people to pursue their fitness and activity goals wherever they are. This unique online platform seamlessly connects sports enthusiasts with sports activity providers so that people can find and book sport activities conveniently.\n\nFacilities can use our SaaS product to manage everything from operations, to advertising classes and even to connect with new potential clients.Players can search, book and pay for classes without ever having to pick up the phone or leave the website. \n\n','Toptable for Sports Facilities','[\"London\"]','PlayEnable'),('Addaero is a web application for athletes and coaches engaged in all levels of fitness to improve the training, weight loss, and fitness experience. \n\nAddaero ameliorates the process with data aggregation, social engagement and individual, group, and self-coaching. \n\nThe athlete engages in meaningful peer, group and coaching interaction through one to one and one to many relationships.\n','Improve health & fitness through technology','[\"Denver\"]','Addaero'),('RapidHealth is a subscription-only, competition-busting online and mobile wellness system for employers and consumers.\n\nIt uses a proprietary mix of Hollywood-quality entertainment, advanced behavioral science, and a truly simple and engaging user-experience.\n\nIt solves the \"deprivation trap\" that trips up almost every diet and health program -- by helping people reshape their emotional patterns and habits. \n\nNew science = better results\n\nTo appreciate it, you must see it in action.','Good health & happiness made easier','[\"New York City\"]','CollaborativeHealth'),('Fit Approach is your healthy community.','Your healthy community.','[]','Fit Approach, LLC'),('At UBmobile we believe that anyone should be able to create their very own mobile app. We help individuals and businesses engage their customers and drive revenue by creating a branded mobile sales channel. We think this makes us unique because our company does the following:\r\n\r\nWe enable businesses to engage consumers on mobile.\r\nMarketers deliver frequent, fun, and entertaining video, as an added value to customers. Customers engage with your brand visually and socially, keeping the app on their device.\r\n\r\nWe make it simple for marketers to publish content.\r\nMarketers can easily push new content to an app, as frequently as desired.\r\n\r\nWe make it easy for customers to buy your product.\r\nCustomers view video and images, then click-to-purchase straight from embedded price tags. No search required.','UBmobile is a user friendly Do-It-Yourself app creation platform.','[\"Redwood City\"]','UBmobile'),(NULL,'Wii Fit for mobile','[]','HasFu Inc (FitFu, YC W11)'),('The Strombss range of products is made from sprouts of millets, wheat, sorghum, green mung, black gram,  chickpeas and Brown rice, soya, Whey Protein, skimmed milk solids, natural flavour extracts. We use the latest technology in processing and packing that help retain the freshness and nutrients of these delicate ingredients. Strombss is an all-natural, pre-cooked, instant powder mix in a single-serve sachet that can be blended in milk or water to make a delicious healthshake. \n\nStrombss+™Active is a rich source of high quality protein (33g/100g), Iron(16mg/100g), Calcium(360mg/100g), Dietary Fiber (6.29g/100g) with NO fat and reduced sugar.\n\nThe other variants are Strombss+™Diet (cocoa, vanilla and Cardamom flavours) that has No Added Sugar and Strombss™Kids for 2-12 year olds(cocoa, vanilla and strawberry flavours).\nOur factory is FDA(India) certified and we follow stringent norms for quality, hygiene and processes, supervised by experienced food technology professionals.\n','a milkshake for good health','[\"Mumbai\"]','Vihaan Natural Healthcare'),('Curl for iPhone is an easy to use exercise log that keeps track of your gym progress.  \n\nOur goal is to make getting fit simple and we are focusing primarily on fitness exercises performed in the gym.  There are great apps that track cardio and diet, but none that deal with fitness exercises performed in the gym.\n\nCurl provides a visually appealing UI and an easy to use logging model that makes entering workout data quick and effortless. ','Mint for Fitness','[\"Los Angeles\"]','Curl'),('- Viral growth- 	             - Month over month auto paying members-\n\n-Online advertising revenue-       - An innovative online Centre for yoga-\n\n- A $10B per year industry- 	         - Social media and mobile application-\n\n- that represent $millions in profits-\n\n= The opportunity that is YogaCentre.com\n\nYogaCentre.com is a virally growing website and lifestyle brand headquartered in San Luis Obispo, California. Yoga Centre, INC was founded and managed by two young entrepreneurs with tremendous passion for yoga and a successful background creating momentum. What began as a single studio with an appealing brand has quickly grown into a much larger opportunity. Yoga Centre INC now encompasses a very successful educational centre and video facility for a complete online yoga experience in YogaCentre.com, YogaCentre.com has the potential to be a $1B+ per year enterprise.\n',' Facebook, meets Youtube, meets the $10.3B powerhouse that is yoga.','[\"San Luis Obispo\"]','Yoga Centre '),('PushPress provides robust, simple, and elegant recurring billing and membership management solutions. Services the niche industry of fitness and health providers.  Our focus is on simplicity and ease of use - something lacking in the competition. ','Redefining Membership Management & Recurring Billing (MindBody)','[\"Culver City\"]','PushPress, Inc.'),('Vitogo is a new approach to fitness based on the simple concept that if you know how to do something, you\'re more likely to succeed at it, and if your customers are succeeding, you\'re more likely to keep them. \n\nVitogo makes achieving fitness goals and preparing for competitions easy and rewarding by giving you the perfect workout program and never leaving you wondering what to do next. \n\nThe Vitogo iOS app is the best way to interact with Vitogo at the gym.','A Personal Trainer at Your Fingertips','[\"New York City\"]','Vitogo'),('Members benefit from streamlined connectivity to fitness professionals and local fitness enthusiasts that they would otherwise have to meet at the gym or on the field. Basic members and professionals benefit from state-of-the art communication and media tools to educate themselves while professionals can set up internal campaigns to help grow their client base which is not currently being done. \n\nOur target market is 98 million Americans ages 18-64 that are engaged in fitness related activity. \n','Imagine Facebook meets LinkedIn for the Fitness Industry','[\"Southern California\"]','FitTogether'),('Just launched a niche, meet-in-person social networking website for active living called Smacktive.com. Smacktive allows users to find like-minded people to experience healthy activities based on deep rooted likes and interests. The website was created to help users across the world begin a healthier, happier lifestyle by sparking new friendships with like-minded people.\n \n“What makes Smacktive special,” says founder & CEO of MindSmack, Sam Feuer, “is the ability for users to search for and join events with people who have things in common, beyond the love of a sport or game or fitness activity.” \n\nIn this digital age, no one should feel lonely. “We built Smacktive to be healthy for the body and for the soul; the chicken soup of social networking, if you will.”\n \nWeb: http://www.Smacktive.com\nFacebook: http://www.Facebook.com/Smacktive\nTwitter: http://www.Twitter.com/Smacktive\nYoutube: http://www.youtube.com/user/SmacktiveVideos','Smacktive.com - meet-in-person network connecting likeminded people 4 activities.','[\"New York City\"]','Smacktive.com'),('Trainersvault is an online community that connects athletes with coaches and trainers.\n\nWe give athletes access to personal trainers, and our mission is to help people live healthier lives through sports and fitness.\n\nComing Summer 2013...\n\n','Find a private sports or fiitness trainer ','[\"San Francisco\"]','TRAINERSvault'),('NoDaysOFF helps its users reach and maintain the body of their dreams through a kickstart 84 Day Program and lifestyle community! \n\nOur specific products are the published NoDaysOFF guide, NDOguide.com web platform and we have a mobile app in development. ','A Fitness Movement for Our Generation! ','[\"Miami\"]','NoDaysOFF '),('MoveMeFit makes it easier and more social to work out anywhere. Don’t have time for a trip to the gym? Raining outside when you want to go for a run? Are studio classes too expensive? Or just want the privacy of working out at home? Whatever your reason is, we want to make sure you are getting the best workout experience at home or on-the-go.\n\nWorking out can be hard, so we want to eliminate your ‘first step’ reasons. Your first step reasons are all the potential reasons you can come up with for not working out. Well, we might not be able to tackle all of them, but we will try our best.\n\nWe’ve partnered with top fitness pros to provide you with unlimited access to hundreds of high quality, easily discoverable, streaming fitness videos right from your home. Need more motivation? You can workout alongside your friends by video chat.\n\nOur mission is simple, to help you get and stay fit. At the end of the day, you need to get moving to be healthy. So let’s go.\n','Online fitness platform','[\"San Francisco\"]','MoveMeFit'),('The Ridekick Trailer has an electric motor and battery inside. It clicks to a bike in seconds, propels you up to 19 mph for ~12 miles, and has room to carry 2 sacks of groceries.\n\nRiders feel the FUN in seconds. At ½ the price of an e-bike, the value is high.\nWe’ve created market disruption.\n\nAbout 40% of the trips we take are under 2 miles from home. We allow people to bike ride without sweat, or up the hill with ease, and provide space for cargo.\nLeave the car in the garage and \'Kick with us!','Electric bike in a trailer - at half the price','[\"Fort Collins\"]','Ridekick International'),('Bodeefit is a health & fitness application that provides daily body weight workouts you can do without any equipment, as well as healthy meal plans & shopping lists.\r\n\r\nBodeefit\'s mission is to remove barriers between people and their health. This means making working out and healthy eating as accessible as possible to people. \r\n\r\nBodeefit is available via the web, mobile, iOS, Android, Windows 8/Phone, and daily emails.','Workouts that don\'t require equipment.','[\"Kansas City, MO\"]','Bodeefit'),('InstaFit is a 10-week online fitness program designed to kickstart our users´ transition into a healthy lifestyle. \r\n\r\nMore info to come.','Online subscription fitness startup in Latam','[\"Mexico, Mexico\"]','InstaFit'),('','','[\"Los Angeles\"]','Vimify'),('Gigabody is initially a web-based streaming platform that brings video fitness classes to people through their internet-enabled devices. We believe a rigorously tested, human-centered approach is the way to transform popular technologies into agents of healthy change.\n\nOur roadmap supports our long-term vision and includes user feedback and engagement triggers, stats and insights, integration of outside health data for a holistic view, and community features to aid in successful habit formation.','Exercise video platform','[\"San Francisco\"]','Gigabody L.L.C.'),('Fittic is an active training plan library that will help you identify workouts and routines aimed at achieving your training goals. Every Fittic training plan outlines starting points, progress indicators, and end goals for runners looking to complete anything from a 5k to a full marathon.','Team Training Plans on your iPhone','[\"Ottawa\"]','Fittic'),('The Active Generation (TAG) will change the way new generations experience physical fitness in the United States. TAG is a classroom community-style fitness platform that provides local and virtual resources for middle school students to stay active in and out of school. Maintaining a dual user experience, TAG brings students together with peers and knowledgeable mentors to collaborate on fitness, while allowing P.E. teachers to manage and share their lessons and engage their students virtually.','TAG is a social/resource platform that will revolutionize U.S. Physical Education.','[\"New York City\"]','The Active Generation'),('3D has arrived! We develop & provide cost effective 3-Dimensional Motion Analysis & Biomechanics applications to physical therapists, chiropractors, strength & conditioning specialists, orthopedic doctors, athletes, the mass market in the form of user friendly low cost applications & ultimately the industrial sector. \n\nOur company is poised to revolutionize the use of 3D and the application of functional training applications leveraging concepts in neuromechanics. ','Take the elevator up from the ground floor with us in motion analysis and biomechanics','[\"Endicott\"]','ZenoLink'),('We empower others power. ','Fab.com for fitness and nutrition.','[\"Seattle\"]','Fitmigo'),('Mint.com for diets','Mint.com for diets','[\"New York City\"]','Zaggy (working title)'),('For busy people in need of inspiration, iMotiva is an ‘active life’ club which motivates you to stay fit and healthy by bringing together all your health information, offering expert guidance, allowing you to compare your fitness and activity anonymously with your peers and rewarding all your activity.\n\niMotiva is available to use worldwide but has a specific focus on UK customers.\n','Get Active.  Get Rewards.  Get Bounts','[\"Oxford\"]','imotiva'),('VitFit provides customized training programs to users anytime, anywhere and coaches them in real time through mp3 downloads. Users follow the coaching, listen to music and meet their fitness goals without planning, thinking or counting. Each user\'s program is created specifically for them to meet their individual needs and match their individual fitness capabilities.\n\nVitFit has 2 distinct sales channels. We provide services direct to the consumer and through fitness clubs. Our tools are easy to use, our music makes the experience fun and our variety keeps workouts interesting and prevents stagnation.','Transforms your digital device into your personal trainer','[\"Philadelphia\"]','MyVitFit'),('BASH Rec Room is an electronic drum studio.  Beginner to expert drummers will come to play drums in classes to live heavy rock music or mp3\'s for fitness & fun in a Manhattan flagship location.  Use 50 sets of noiseless electronic drum kits and headphones makes possible a communal rock and roll ruckus.  Drummers can sit on an exercise ball, adding a fun bounce, or a conventional throne.  Also, drummers can add weights to their wrists, hands, and drumsticks & burn as many as 700 cals in 45 mins!','Rock Concert Drumming Simulation Fun & Exercise Center','[\"New York City\"]','BASH Rec Room'),('RX Magazine is the first CrossFit and Functional Fitness Magazine in Spanish. We promote a Paleo Lifestyle, Evolutionary Medicine and Primal Nutrition. The only specialized media in Latin America focused on Functional Fitness, Strength & Conditioning and Weight Lifting.','The first CrossFit and Functional Fitness Magazine in Spanish','[\"Monterrey\"]','RX Magazine'),('Runnit is an iPhone app that rewards users with free products, discounts and other benefits for going running. The app is free to download, and helps users stay motivated when they run. Runnit uses GPS to track progress, and users can only unlock rewards by completing the required distance. Runnit generates revenue by charging brands a fixed fee per reward claimed.','Rewarding users for going running','[\"London\"]','Runnit'),('Subscribers pay $20/month for a curated box of unique snacks that are paleo friendly. We launched with 62 subscribers in September and have averaged 32% month-over-month growth. We have 420 subscribers receiving our May box. http://box.PaleoPax.com\n\nWe launched an online marketplace for Paleo snack foods on April 1st. It also has a private \"bulk\" section for owners of gyms (particularly Crossfit boxes) who want to buy wholesale and sell directly to their members. http://PaleoPax.com\n\n','Paleo Snack Subscriptions, Online Sales, and Crossfit Distributor','[\"Syracuse\"]','PaleoPax'),('Crush Fitness is building an online functional fitness program that actually has a brain.  Currently, the only method of receiving \"functional fitness\" instruction is by hiring a personal trainer.  Crush Fitness fills the gap for people who cannot afford this expensive instruction by customizing and delivering a fresh, new workout, every day to the user\'s computer or mobile device.  100 levels of intensity and thousands of videos will keep the variety flowing and the results showing.','Your Daily Functional Fitness Plan.','[\"Washington, DC\"]','CrushFit'),('Our vision is for FitUsIn to be the leading booking platform for fitness activities globally.\n\nThe website and smartphone application provides total flexibility, allowing consumers to workout anywhere, anytime - at the best possible rate!\n\nOur customers love FitUsIn because they can choose from hundreds of gyms, group classes and personal trainers. They can quickly compare facilities and book discounted passes instantly.\n\nThe result is a new way of accessing fitness activities - no more joining fees, inductions or long term contracts! With FitUsIn, everything can be compared and booked online to provide the highest level of convenience.\n\nFitness businesses love listing on FitUsIn because we help them make better use of their facilities, increase their user base and their revenue.\n\nWe have a commission-based model, where FitUsIn retains a percentage of each booking that goes through the platform.\n\nwww.fitusin.com','Hassle free fitness deals','[\"Sydney\"]','FitUsIn'),('Trainer+ is a SaaS platform that enables personal trainers to deliver ongoing value to clients between face-to-face interactions. From a central dashboard, trainers can: push exercise routines; monitor client progress; measure their own impact and service a broader client base than ever before.','Scalable service tools for Personal Trainers','[\"Toronto\"]','TrainerPlus'),('Achieving fitness goals requires peers and a place to meet. An online studio for anytime+anywhere fitness with peer groups for a better life. Motivation is driven by three key features: content, social interaction and tracking data.  Fitness content is any program which can be delivered via video such as pilates, yoga, high impact aerobics, speed bikes, treadmill programs and more. A webcam monitors motion using proprietary algorithms to create actionable data shared with peers.','Virtual Fitness Studio','[\"Blacksburg\"]','KinectHealth'),('myPower is a running companion that clips to your hip and captures your kinetic energy as you run. myPower stores this energy so you can use it to charge your smartphone or other mobile device later in the day. In essence, myPower is a rechargeable battery that you never have to worry about recharging--as long as you keep running. Forty-five minutes of running with myPower can give your iPhone an extra 7 to 8 hours of battery life, and running with myPower for a year can offset the carbon footprint of itself and the device you charge with it. At about the size of a small cellphone, myPower is comfortable, stylish, and can be worn when biking or walking as well.','Recharge your smartphone by running','[\"Chicago\"]','myPower'),('GLocker is an application dedicated to promoting healthier living through social media and photo-sharing. The main goal of our platform is to pressure users to improve their lives. With our unique and first-of-its-kind application, we will empower our users and offer them the tools they need to increase their fitness knowledge, eat healthy, and receive gratification for all of their hardwork. There are many fitness applications out there today that are formative and helpful, however getting you to actually work-out and live the lifestyle is the tricky part. With GLocker we will offer the informational aspect while also offering the peer aspect to actually give users the extra push they need to improve their health.  \n\nLiving a healthy & nutritious lifestyle is about to become addictive, fun, and gratifying. ','Eat. Exercise. Share. ','[\"New York City\"]','GLocker '),('Ensa provides a single point for users to combine both wellness and clinical data for the purpose of receiving real-time contextual recommendations via our rules engine. Ensa\'s recommendations are social, mobile, & real time. All healthcare data now becomes meaningful advice. This promotes a healthier lifestyle, and increases patient wellness without always having to see a doctor.','Health and fitness apps and real time advice sync\'d','[\"New York City\"]','Ensa'),('MedTechCollective develops  a cloud based health  and fitness analytics platform  that processes data from  available fitness sensors for health and fitness analysis on a new level to provide users with ability to achieve health and fitness goals faster without overtraining in an optimal way','Predictive health and fitness analytics. Cloud and mobile based platform ','[\"Princeton\"]','MedTechCollective'),('We do the impossible.','We do the impossible.','[\"Chicago\"]','Impossible Ventures'),('Exclusively focused on the morbidly obese, Downsize Fitness offers online/offline fitness training, nutritional guidance and a support community resulting in 4,000 pounds lost between our 2 gyms in Chicago and Dallas.','Technology-enabled fitness, nutrition and support for the morbidly obese','[\"Chicago\"]','Downsize Fitness'),('SWERVE Fitness brings to market the first team-inspired, indoor cycling experience. The unique team structure of the class motivates individual riders to reach their highest potential during this full-body workout. SWERVE utilizes innovative technology to track all performance metrics of riders. Our studio is located at 30 West 18th Street in the Flatiron District in NYC.','Fitness Tech Startup','[\"New York City\"]','SWERVE Fitness'),('box-planner is CRM for CrossFit box (box=gym) owners and members. CrossFit is one of the fastest growing sports (8 years ago there were 20 gyms, today there are 8500). Out of 50m gym members in the US, >1 million are CrossFitters. CrossFit is growing 25% annually, because it focuses on personal training, tracking of results, competition and community. Reebok\'s annual marketing budget for CrossFit alone is $50m (!). We are making the interaction between owners and members more efficient by making it easy to manage memberships, track results and compete with other members. We aim to leverage the rapid growth of CrossFit to build a profitable beach-head and then expand to related competitive fitness verticals that add up to a total addressable market of $30 billion. Our strategy is to offer a free CRM for box owners in order to get a maximum amount of athletes on the platform. The average daily usage by our users today is 4:35min.We offer premium accounts for athletes and box owners','CRM for CrossFit box owners and athletes','[\"London\"]','box-planner'),('Fueled app is a workout app aimed at micro workouts spread throughout your day. Most people sit for long hours at work and then don\'t have time to go to the gym. Fueled has 30-60 second micro-workouts that add up to a full workout by the end of the day.','mobile micro-workouts','[\"Toledo\"]','Fueled'),(NULL,'Workout tracking, marketing, and retention software for CrossFit gyms.','[\"Vancouver\"]','SocialWOD'),('A one stop shop for the booming Crossfit market and garage home fitness enthusiast.  We serve end to end with a comprehensive selection of equipment and consulting services as well.','Crossfit and Strength Conditioning Equipment for the masses','[\"Toronto\"]','Primal Athletes'),('MOREFIT is a series of progressive annual events in multiple cities where individuals compete for cash and product awards for the greatest improvement in their wellness. Competitors must sustain their achieved wellness for several years to fully benefit from the prizes and lifestyle advancement. A variety of events span a 9 month period culminating in a grand finale. Events feature fashion, runway, music, athletics, arts, cuisine, training and education. Biometrics are measured along the way with the those showing the greatest positive change advancing through multiple elimination rounds. Individual competitors select their favorite charity as a beneficiary of their fundraising efforts.    \r\n\r\nMorefit is attainable by anyone. It involves individuals, personal trainers, nutritionists and health clubs. It stimulates charitable giving and promotes social networking. It rewards participants for attaining goals AND maintaining wellness into the future and elicits permanent positive change.','Sustainable Wellness Challenge rewarding competitors for biometric improvement','[\"Minneapolis\"]','Morefit'),('Recent studies show beetroot juice can:\r\nEnhance exercise performance\r\nReduce resting blood pressure\r\nLower oxygen cost of sub-maximal exercise. (i.e. enhance muscle efficiency) \r\n\r\nBeetBomb is a concentrated shot that provides a nitrate-rich beetroot juice in a convenient and innovative form.\r\n','Natural Beet Juice shot for natural energy and endurance','[\"Los Angeles\"]','Beet Bomb'),('Leannerds provides meal plans for overall health, muscle gain or fat loss to college students based on their campus dining halls. For free. On a daily basis.','Meal plans based on college dining halls ','[\"Wellesley\"]','Leannerds'),('TrackFaster is the only wellness program tool that is effective in helping users reach the health goals that matter to them, is scaleable, and provides a high ROI to you, the employer.\n\nUsers are successful because our product combines three powerful approaches:\n1. Evidence-based fitness and nutrition education\n2. Validated behavioral change techniques\n3. Our proprietary course-correcting algorithm\n\nThis combination ensures that each user is always getting information that is both practical and relevant to them.\n\nTrackFaster’s alpha test is currently focused on fat loss goals. Current wellness programs average less than 1 lb of weight loss per year, but our alpha users have achieved an average of 7lbs of weight loss in just two months. Research shows that the health improvements we provide can save employers up to $1650 per overweight employee per year from reduced healthcare costs and improvements in absenteeism and presenteeism.','Redefining Corporate Wellness','[\"Chicago\"]','TrackFaster'),('Our software was developed for fitness studios, personal trainers and athletes. We have a rich functionality for each group:\n\nFitness Studios or Personal Trainer:\n- Manage the athletes and memberships\n- Training and diet plans \n- Personalised equipment and devices profiles\n- Courses management\n- Question/Answer from athletes\n- Internal messaging\n- Advertising\n- Statistics\n\nAthletes:\n- Training and diet plans\n- Acess to integrate 3rd party fitness devices\n- Communication with trainer\n- Studio entrance with mobile phone\n- Registration for courses\n- Fitness studio statistics\n- Statistics','Online plattform for connecting fitness studios/trainers with athletes!','[\"Germany\"]','Fitgeon'),('FitFriend is like a stopwatch on your iPhone. It not only takes splits, but it\'s the fastest, easiest, and most efficient tool to train with.\n\nRunners need split timing for interval training. Currently anyone past the level of a \"casual\" or \"beginner\" runner, still uses their stopwatch for training. Even though there\'s a bucketload of fitness apps out there. Weird? \n\nNot exactly - these existing apps don\'t cater to any runner past that level of \"beginner\". \n\nFitFriend is filling that void. Founded by a mobile engineer, with almost 2 decades of running experience. \n\nRunners who use coaches, or even some kind of mild training program, train with interval sessions. Any runner that has goals, trains with interval sessions. FitFriend is bringing this to the iPhone for the first time, so runners can finally transition from using their watches. \n','Stopwatch app for runners','[\"Toronto\"]','FitFriend'),('Etiquette Education for all levels - Ages 4 to Adult\n\nAt Ladies & Gentlemen-In-Training we... \n\nPromote Manners, Respect, Self-Esteem, Compassion & Confidence. \nWe Teach Poise, Grace, Elegance, Gallantry & Chivalry.\n\nWe are Creative, Independent Thinking Leaders. \n\nWe Offer Helpful Advice and Encouragement. We Expose our students to New Ideas and Concepts.  We Provide and Develop Positive Role Models. \n \nWe Support the Value of Having Faith.  We offer Guidance & Patience.  \nWe Inspire Greatness.','Etiquette Education, Finishing School, Building Character & Intelligence','[\"Toronto\"]','LaGiT Etiquette Academy'),('Video hosting made easy with ZenVideoCloudTM\r\n\r\nBuild your business with a simple and cost effective HD video streaming solution. The best part? We\'ve already ironed out all the kinks for you.\r\n\r\nEmbeddable HD video player\r\nSecure hosting\r\nCredit card processing\r\nPayroll solutions\r\n\r\nAll without the hassle and cost of custom web-development.','Finally! A monetize-able Video Hosting Solution for the Health and Wellness Industry. ','[\"San Luis Obispo\"]','Zen Video Cloud '),('8 BitFit is a retro-themed smartphone game played by running in the real world. \n\nIt tracks run time, pace and distance, which are transformed into points, levels, achievements and multi-player quests, all set within a rich gameworld of robots, pixels, energy, and vintage sneakers.\n\nGameplay is grounded in real fitness accomplishments, determined by player fitness level. Each game world is 26.6 miles long; players must travel the distance of four marathons to defeat the game.\n\nRunning stats are tracked and stored within the app, and optionally synced to Runkeeper.\n\nPlayers can easily invite friends to 2-player fitness quests for bonus points. Accomplishments and trophies can be posted to  social media.\n\n8 BitFit is inspired by the simple yet clever and highly engaging games of the 1980\'s and early 1990\'s. It features hundreds of hidden bonuses that players unlock by running, along with exclusive unlockable mini-games that can be played anytime (not just by running).','Don\'t just track your fitness, play it.','[\"Burlington, VT\"]','8 BitFit'),('A mobile application that lets people who like to work out or play a sport find people to play with or work out with through their existing social network or their nearby location. \r\n\r\nThrough Qotrain, users can connect with their facebook friends and friends of friends and invite people who are interested in the same activities at the same location at the same times to workout or play a sport with them. \r\n\r\nUsers can also book venues, rent equipment or form teams to play larger group sports with. ','Find workout and sports partners','[\"Bangalore\"]','coTrain'),('Rocket Sports is an online platform to help people (a) find and access sports at a grass roots/amateur level and (b) manage sports teams, events, clubs and leagues.\n\nWe aim to remove all barriers to entry, help reduce dropout rates, and make the lives of organisers of any sporting activities easier.\n\nRocketSports.co.uk is an interactive, online management & payment platform for sports enthusiasts, instructors, managers, clubs & organisations. We facilitate the organisation of games, events, competitions, and leagues, enabling the payment of fees and allowing easy, efficient interaction between users whilst allowing like-minded individuals to find, see, investigate and request to join your event, team, club or organisation.','Find & connect online, meet & play offline | An interactive online sports platform','[\"London\"]','RocketSports'),('JoggingBuddy.com is a free website that allows members to find other members to go running with.  I launched the site in September 2008 and now have members in 92 countries.  Members can:\n- Search for running partners\n- Search for events\n- Search for local running routes\n- Log their runs\n- Search news, reviews and advice sections\n- Use the Forum\n','JoggingBuddy.com helps runners find other runners to train with.  Now in 92 countries','[\"United Kingdom\"]','JoggingBuddy'),('This site allows members to find other members to go cycling with.','Social network for Cyclists','[\"United Kingdom\"]','mycyclingbuddy'),('We partner with pro athletes and their trainers, across all sports (NBA, NFL, NHL, MLB, etc.). They give us the athletes real off-season training programs. We then do a photo/video shoot with the athlete. The program, along with instructional videos and photos is available online and via mobile apps. Customers can record results, track progress, etc. Customers are the 60 million young athletes in the US. Programs allow young athletes to connect with their idols, and of course, train correctly. ','Go Pro or Go Home','[\"Boston\"]','Go Pro Workouts'),('Juicify makes staying on top of your nutrition easy by offering users the ability to see detailed nutrition labels for all of our juice and smoothie recipes. \n\nWe are also two weeks away from releasing a feature allowing our 20,000+ users to create, name, and share their own recipes complete with photos and nutrition labels!\n\nOnce we acquire financing we will quickly roll out our next planned features and in app purchases.\n\nScreenshots not uploading correctly, so you can view them here: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/juicify-50+-healthy-juice/id601364396?mt=8','Nutrition. Simplified.','[\"San Francisco\"]','Juicify'),(NULL,'','[\"New York City\"]','SleepBot'),('The average gym loses nearly $800,000 yearly due to member attrition.  Group fitness classes are gyms most powerful member retention tool.  \n\npeerFit improves member retention with a fitness application that makes group fitness easy to access and share. Using digital triggers and social integration peerFit keeps a member deeply engaged with their gym.\n\n20 million Americans use group fitness a month. peerFit users review classes they\'ve attended allowing others to make well-informed decisions.  \n','tripadvisor for group fitness classes','[\"Gainesville\"]','peerFit'),('Carrot Gyms is the only gym membership for business travelers. Traditional gym memberships, hotel gyms, and guest passes are poor quality, too expensive, or too inconvenient. We help the busy traveler stay healthy on the road. Carrot Gyms lets you use any participating gym in any city.','The Gym Membership For Business Travelers','[\"Washington, DC\"]','Carrot Gyms'),('China\'s international fitness, nutrition, and lifestyle blog.  Curated content from barbell to biochemistry.\n\nWe provide frequent fitness recommendations and sociopolitical commentary related to health in China.  The Jianshen Community create our value; our team writes what you want to read, and we incorporate suggested topics regularly!','China\'s fitness, nutrition, lifestyle blog.  Curated content from barbell to biochemistry.','[\"Shanghai\"]','健神 Jianshen Health'),('In a mobile UI/UX, we will bring a person\'s fitness apps and devices together to form their complete fitness profile. Using algorithms developed by Jesse Kropelnick for elite and amateur triathletes, we will create a klout-like fitness score from a user\'s quantified data. Tracking this score over time, allows us to deliver targeted editoria to users to support them in achieving their fitness goals.\n\nPrototype KPI\'s:\n8333 active users\n$85K revenue per month\n\nStrategic Equity Investor:\nBrand Connections come in and commit as a strategic equity partner in a services for equity arrangement. We estimate with Brand Connections involvement the funding need on the seed round is potentially halved. www.brandconnections.com','what\'s your fitness klout?','[\"New York City\"]','aktiv8.me'),(NULL,'To empower entrepreneurs to stay healthy and fit while helping them stay motivated.','[\"Austin\"]','FundFit Collective'),('The 1-sentence elevator pitch goes something like this: We want to help you stop making excuses. \n\nWhat we are doing at DamnFit is trying to identify the types of incentive that foster self-motivation. \n\nOur first product is a mobile app that will allow users to raise money for charity by completing self-assigned fitness goals. Not only will users be able to help others simply by being active, but also they will find themselves a part of a team fighting for a common goal. We believe that by coupling social incentive with philanthropic inspiration in a team setting that we can change bad habits. \n\nWe hope to build an entire community of individuals looking to better their own lives and the lives of others. ','Fitness For A Cause','[\"Nashville\"]','DamnFit'),('iFity video personal training done right. \n\niFity is not just another workout app.  iFity is a personalized training service where the coaches deliver value both via one on one video training and with custom programs and workouts subscribers follow on their own. \n