at. Kosha covers are Eco-friendly, slip resistant, water/odor resistant, anti bacterial, and the best part can be thrown in the washer and dryer! Never will someone need to clean or repeatedly have to buy a new mat. \n\nWe have 2 versions: 1) A Kosha Cover 2) An easily transportable Kosha Cover. This cover has an attachable yoga bag that the cover easily rolls into. \n\n','First ever cover for Yoga and Pilates mats','[\"Los Angeles\"]','Kosha'),('Our site creates customized on-demand training programs for the time crunched triathlete who can\'t follow a \"canned\" plan. ','Express Triathlon Training','[\"Dallas\"]','TriDaily'),('fitChallenge: the app that motivates you get fit by challenging a friend to an exercise competition\n\nBased on the board game, The Fitness Challenge, featured on ABC, NBC, CBS, People, Oprah’s O, and Health Magazine.\n\n• Dozens of workouts with exercise times by fitness level\n• Notifications immediately notify players of workouts\n• The Workout Calendar tracks both player\'s workouts\n• Post workouts to Facebook and Twitter\n• \"Workout Stats\" track workouts\n• Trainer screens - offer help and tips','Exercise with Friends App: \"fitChallenge\"','[\"Minneapolis\"]','The Fitness Challenge'),('Black Forest Accelerator by Team/E is the first of its kind accelerator program in South-West Germany. We believe that this picturesque region provides great possibilities to founders, who want to work in a calm, natural and beautiful environment. \nWe provide 12.500€, office space in the zeit.areal in Lahr, mentoring from renowned business leaders and also world class athletes and media attention. The 3-month program will end with a Demo Day where participating Start-Ups can pitch their projects and get in contact with potential investors.\n','a Black Forest based mentorship driven accelerator program for Health & Fitness Start-Ups','[\"Lahr\"]','Black Forest Accelerator by Team/E'),('Anchor Fitness is an online health and fitness company that will d