culpting so that you get the look that you want.  We train you in all areas of fitness that is safe for your body and allows you to see results faster through improving your body\'s neuromuscular communication.\n\nThe JFit4Me Nutrition Program helps you build your own diet plan that caters to your lifestyle, budget, and fitness goals so that you lose weight and maintain it for a lifetime.  \n\nSo no more 30-day plans! Fitness is a lifestyle!\n\n\n\n','Virtual Fitness Trainer By A Certfied Fitness Professonal','[\"Durham\"]','Jazmin Fitness'),('bodyADDICTS offers the seamless delivery of Elite \"Train Anywhere\" Fitness Professionals to Eco-Friendly Training Locations: In-Home, public fitness centers, parks, small private functional training studios, and small gyms. Interactive fitness profiles allow for scheduling, tracking tools, and on-line follow up support. bodyADDICTS customers are anyone on the go, seeking motivation, or an economical alternative to the large retail health clubs.','Delivering functional fitness to Eco-Friendly locations.','[\"New York City\"]','bodyADDICTS'),('STORY is an elegant, thin e-ink wristband whose picture gradually changes over the course of your day.\r\n\r\nIt learns your fitness level, and then slowly and gradually increases your daily goal.\r\n\r\nIt will work seamlessly and without setup for anyone ages 2 to 102.\r\n\r\nIf your fitness level for the day was below what STORY thinks you should have done, you go to bed with the picture unfinished.\r\n\r\nEach night, the picture resets to give you a fresh start in the morning.\r\n\r\nIt is an unusual conversation piece and when somebody asks you about it, you can hit a button that will demo a time-lapsed version what you did YESTERDAY.\r\n\r\nSo if you know people are likely to ask you about it, you will be motivated to finish out the picture every day.\r\n\r\nThe flexible E-ink display is like the one used on the popular CST-01 watch shown on Kickstarter.\r\n\r\nThe picture will first be drawn in black silhouette, then gradually begin highlighting in red.','Thin, elegant illustrated wearable activity band','[\"Chicago\"]','Gamma Wearables'),(NULL,'Securing and marketing preferred rates for fitness professionals','[\"Montreal\"]','Fitness Pro Deals'),('We develop a revolutionary software for gyms, which gives the customers a more engaging, motivational, enjoyable experience, resulting a higher level of satisfaction and retention. Furthermore it increases gym\'s margins through lowered staff requirements.\n\nGymTeq has the following USPs:\n\n- GymTeq motivates gym-customers better, so they are more successfull and as a result customer retention, loyalty is higher.\n\n- Through automatization of customer handling GymTeq reduces the need of staff, what helps to increase margins.\n\n-Independent from sports equipment manufacturers. Applicable with existing equipment.\n\n- New sensor technique to improve correct use of sports equipment.\n\n- With NFC cards we identify the customers at all sports equipment, automatically distribute and control tasks, and follow the execution of individual training plans.\n\n','Revolutionary software for gyms. Results higher customer loyalty and margins.','[\"Budapest\"]','Desksell Ltd.'),('Our online golf ChiroFit program gives you a series of tests as to your strength, flexibility and balance – your result places you in one of three categories beginner, intermediate or professional golfer and gives you personalized exercises to come up to the next level – your first evaluation is $99.00 on line and your re-evaluation after you think you have improved is only $35.00 - Roger Podmore Certified Master Golf Teacher has been using GFTG for many years at: www.golfbiomechanics.com.au\n','Better Body, Better Golf - through simple & cost effective online biomechanical solutions','[\"Walnut Creek\"]','Get Fit To Golf'),('i.strive.to is a tool that helps you define, track, and analyze all of your goals, and other personal matrices in one place.\n\n','Personal Analytics Platform','[\"New York City\"]','i.strive.to'),('The Products\n\n1. The Titles\nCPL publishes specialist digital magazine titles focussed on niche, but rapidly growing, sports sectors. Cyclo and TriGear are our first title across all platforms [Web, iPad and iPhone]. The remaining titles are designed and ready to launch. \n\nCPL titles deliver revenue in three areas: \n•	Advertising – banner and pre-roll video on website, \n•	Affiliate Sales – share of revenue for click-through sales\n•	Subscription - fee for magazine app issue\n\nThe title launch schedule is: \n•	2011 – Cycling\n•	2013 – Triathlon\n•	2013 – Rugby\n•	2014 – Running\n•	2015 – TBD\n\n2. The Technology Platform - COPE\nCPL identified an opportunity for a multi-platform publishing system to address the problems of the Publishing industry when moving to digital. In development since 2009, the platform began operations in Sept 2011. The platform provides advantages in: low costs of production, Speed to market, Future proof [each component can be ‘unplugged’ and replaced]\n','Digital Magazine Publishing','[\"Cambridge, UK\"]','CPL'),('Paleo produces minimalist footwear with articulated toes. Picture a \"foot glove\" rather than a minimalist shoe or toe-shoe. Our goal is to maximize the potential of the human body, not to hinder it with complicated lacing systems that bind the foot and intricate suspension designs that interfere with the mind/body connection. Paleo\'s first line of footwear will be more flexible, washable, breathable, water-resistant and affordable than what\'s out there now. There\'s no gimmicks, no shocks, no air bubbles; just two years of product development behind our idea to ensure that every pair we sell helps gets people excited about fitness (from yogis to ultra marathoners). go to www.paleobarefootwear.com to learn more about our product and barefoot training','Minimalist Footwear','[\"San Francisco\"]','Paleo Barefootwear'),('ChatterDoc p