eate a fun environment of constant progress; to maintain education as our primary goal for both coaches and clients.','Revolutionary fitness (Crossfit)','[\"Bangkok\"]','Crossfit Inline'),('I am trying to build a women\'s only bootcamp that is challenging, affordable and fun. There is only one operating in my area (Booty Camp) but it\'s far to expensive, and it caters to it\'s weakest members.\n\nWe believe that women can be strong, fitness warriors and we want to start an affordable bootcamp that is challenging and gets results.','Women\'s Only Bootcamp','[\"Edmonton\"]','Fitness Amazons'),('TotalWOD develops and markets apps (iOS, Android, web) for CrossFit gyms and their members. The apps are designed to take advantage of the community and competition nature of CrossFit workouts (WODs) and CrossFit gyms. The apps allow for the tracking, logging and comparing of WOD performance amongst friends and fellow gym members.  The focus from a revenue standpoint is on gyms where the apps will be free but a monthly usage fee per gym member in the TotalWOD database will be assessed.','Unique CrossFit-related apps','[\"Los Angeles\"]','TotalWOD'),('Frabbit is a fitness social network that will inspire and motivate people to reach their true fitness potential.\n\nWe are trying to create a personalized workout experience for people used to taking group fitness classes. At Frabbit people can discover and sign up for cool new workouts, find workouts that make sense to them and get encouraged by their friends and health industry professionals\n\nWe are Fat Rabbit and we get people in shape using data.\n\n\n\n\n\n','Fitocracy + Foursquare + MindBody','[\"Philadelphia\"]','Frabbit'),('Recognizing the synergies between cheer motions & free weight training, FIT 2 CHEER, a company specializing in the fusion of two global industries: FITNESS & CHEER LEADING, invented PoundPoms (weighted cheer pom poms) created a new workout (CHEER CAMP) and formed Cutz Camp a sports specific cheer condi