d around a basic yet powerful premise to empower our community with safe, sustainable and highly effective juice detox systems.','Responsible Juice Detox','[\"Chicago\"]','Urban Renuil'),('Yibbly, the best way to find, share and create ANY Sport or Fitness Activity via mobile. Make a FREE mobile shop and sell your merch.\r\n\r\n','meetup with foursquare and shopify','[\"New York City\"]','Yibbly!'),('Music can have an incredible influence on our activities, behavior and mood.  Rollbeat technology significantly improves workout effectiveness and fun and answers the following:\n\n1.	New wearable patches, shirts and bands for reading body metrics during workout, are in rapid raise. Sales will surpass $1 billion in 2014. Their data can and should be used for creating perfect playlists.\n\n2.	52% of people that work-out with music find it an annoying task, try to avoid it and ask for an alternative.\n \n3.	The playlists they create have a poor to average impact on workout effectiveness and fun.\n\nRollbeat is professionally selected, processed and handled for a specific workout, user’s metrics and taste and is very easy to use. \n\nIt results in improved effectiveness and higher energy. No similar product or service is offered today.\n\nRollbeat will become essential as shoes and water for over 300 million working-out people.','Transforming music into positive ‘steroids’ for workout. ','[\"Tel Aviv-yafo\"]','Rollbeat'),('Finding fitness classes nearby is currently inconvenient. Working professionals & corporate travellers are generally time poor & want to utilize their time productively.\r\n\r\nFitness Freak will provide an efficient and cost effective online marketing channel for independent fitness businesses and discovery booking portal for the consumer looking to book into classes with low occupancy. Classes currently average 70% capacity.\r\n\r\nTo become the one stop shop for the fitness enthusiast; booking into spaces in classes, keeping users up to date with all the latest fitness news, classes, reviews and workout trends in order to create an aspirational fitness brand.\r\n\r\nFitness Freak was the first website of it’s kind to market, launching with bookable one-off rate fitness classes in December 2012.','The only way to discover & book fitness classes online','[\"London\"]','Fitness Freak'),('Connect with other athletes to play pick-up sports when and where you want to. Simply click to join or create a game for you and others to enjoy. Game invites can be sent to anyone with a phone number or email, making this app truly cross platform. Features are being added to gamify the user experience and allow athletes to track and compete based on achievements made in real life. The app is currently in Beta on iOS 7.','Foursquare for sports','[\"Washington, DC\"]','League Warrior'),('Fitsplore is an upcoming website with companion mobile apps that are aimed at making fitness more accessible to people. In doing so, Fitsplore enables people to lead healthier lives by staying or being more active, whether it\'s locally or on the go.','fitness on the fly','[\"San Francisco\"]','Fitsplore'),('a biosensor for fitness use','microwave based sensor','[\"Tel Aviv-yafo\"]','Sensifree'),(NULL,'Prevent Genetic Disease before Pregnancy with a DNA Test','[\"Redwood City\"]','Counsyl'),('','','[\"San Francisco\"]','Kapor Capital'),('At Felicis Ventures, our Mission is to back the world’s most iconic companies of today and tomorrow. Our founders have a passion for product, thinking out of the box to solve hard problems and dominate critical markets. Since 2006 we have invested in over 100 companies, 28 of which have been acquired by industry leaders such as Google, Apple, Facebook, Microsoft, Disney, eBay, Twitter, Intuit, Groupon and AT&T.','Backing the Iconic Companies of Today and Tomorrow','[\"Silicon Valley\"]','Felicis Ventures'),('We connect mental health consumers, providers, and health plans for online therapy and telepsychiatry. \n\nConsumers can search for providers, view video introductions, schedule online appointments, take assessments, and receive private mental health care anywhere at anytime.\n\nProviders can build a free profile, manage their online practice, and deliver HIPAA-compliant online care.\n \nHealth plans buy access to our provider network and technology to improve the cost, quality, and access of care.','Online mental healthcare','[\"Redwood City\"]','Breakthrough.com'),('At Ginger.io, we are on a mission to change population health. \n\nAs a spin-off of MIT\'s Media Lab, we use sensor data and machine learning to build a \'check-engine light\' for a person\'s health. Our platform is designed to help chronic patients, their caregivers and providers improve care through better connections.\n\nGinger.io is currently working with leading US healthcare institutions, has won industry awards, and has been featured in the Economist, New York Times, and Businessweek.','Behavioral Analytics for Population Management','[\"San Francisco\"]','Ginger.io'),('Medigram is a HIPAA-compliant group messaging platform for health care professionals (i.e. doctors, nurses, etc). It is cross-platform. Download the app, sign up, verify your identity, and start talking with colleagues within 60 seconds.\n\nWe bring in-hospital realtime messaging with referral communication software together under one platform.\n\nOur background is from Stanford Med and CS. We have 6+ years of hospital experience, and experience building HIPAA-compliant systems and mobile software.','HIPAA-Compliant Group Communication Platform, YC W2012, StartX F2011','[\"Los Altos\"]','Medigram'),(NULL,'','[\"Boston\"]','Polaris Partners'),('AgileMD delivers high-yield, point-of-care, clinical knowledge tailored to each users setting. AgileMD is designed for clinical rigor and optimized for low connectivity settings.','High-yield clinical knowledge. Mobile.','[\"San Francisco\"]','AgileMD'),('Flatiron Health was started in 2012 by two