nge any amounts of data (text, binary - images/videos) over very slow networks. It can applied to a whole range of industries like Microfinance, Healthcare. \n\nThe product consists of mobile (Android) and cloud technologies, with a Do-It-Yourself approach to allow for customization as per requirement.','To provide high quality service to bottom of the pyramid customers using mobile and cloud.','[\"Bangalore\", \"India\"]','Artoo'),('Zephyr is a leading provider of real-time test management solutions. Enterprises rely on Zephyr to get instant updates regarding the quality and status of their software projects. Zephyr\'s solutions integrate with Atlassian tools and various automation frameworks, giving project teams complete traceability over their requirements and defects. \n\nZephyr Enterprise Edition is used by over 200 of the Global 2000 and Zephyr for JIRA is the #1 Top Grossing JIRA add-on in the Atlassian Marketplace.','','[\"Newark, CA\"]','Zephyr'),('RegulatoryBinder saves hospitals time and money spent on research documentation.\n\nThe Clinical Trials Transformation Initiative and Institute of Medicine, however, have recently said that clinical research is a \"paper-based, slow, & costly\" \"burden\" on hospitals already under increasing cost-constraints.\n\nLimited revenue-generators at hospitals, spend copious amount of time managing printed pages of regulatory documentation in three-ring regulatory binders! This represents a $50B documentation opportunity cost.\n\nRegulatoryBinder has developed a novel SaaS solution that enables staff to reduce the time spent on research documentation by 33%, resulting $15B in potential annual savings. Only RegulatoryBinder is designed for hospital regulatory binders and bundles compliance services to ensure that software is compliant with FDA eRecord regulations from the very first login. Existing software can take $3-5M and over 1 year to customize, validate, and implement.','Document clinical studies better','[\"Cleveland\"]','RegulatoryBinder'),('State-of-the-art and up-to-date knowledge base around pharmacogenomics. With the ability to deliver to and integrate with many different kinds of customer applications.','Pharmacogenetic Knowledge-as-a-Service','[\"Boston\"]','PanGenX'),('Hospitals purchase $200 billion in medical devices each year. Medical device companies spend more to sell a product than to manufacture it. Hospitals need to save money. Medical device companies need to sell products efficiently.  With Curvo, they both win.','','[\"Indiana\"]','Curvo Labs'),('Linked Senior Inc., a resident engagement solution provider, helps senior care leaders improve the quality of life of their residents. By using technology to support programming, therapy & wellness the service opens communities to the world while helping management improve resident & family satisfaction, productivity and efficiencies.','Engagement solution for the senior housing market (AL, SNF, Memory Care)','[\"Washington, DC\"]','Linked Senior'),('Medicinia is being launched with the goal of becoming the most disruptive healthcare company in Latin America by providing an alternative healthcare delivery model, based on online, high-frequency interactions to complement the traditional office-based, low-frequency model, increasing doctor productivity and patient satisfaction. It does so through a questions and answers platform to connect patients with doctors and general practioners with specialists.','The online hub for doctor-patient interactions in Brazil ','[\"Sao Paulo\"]','Medicinia'),('Qikwell is SAAS service for healthcare providers that helps them engage with their patients via voice calls, mobile and web better while saving them doctors\' time and helping patients achieve better health outcomes.','Patient Relation Management Done Right','[\"Bangalore\"]','Qikwell '),('Our platform engages cancer patients in their care by combining evidence-based guidelines, clinical trials, and patient preferences to ge