-diagnosis and preventive medicine. Via the website, Internet users can obtain preliminary information regarding potential conditions, and then make an appointment with a suitable physician.\n\nSee how it works: http://symptomate.com','Supporting medical diagnostics using state-of-the-art artificial intelligence solutions','[\"Warsaw\"]','Infermedica'),('Health Business Intelligence Corp (Health BI) was created by two physicians and two Health IT veterans. Our strength is in developing HIPAA-compliant messaging, care coordination, care transitions and patient engagement solutions for the healthcare vertical. Our tools are designed to enable providers and payers to coordinate care by engaging patients in the decision-making process. ','Care Coordination, Population Health, Care Transitions','[\"Scottsdale\"]','Health Business Intelligence Corp.'),('Pangianet is a comprehensive digital healthcare solution for patients, healthcare professionals, & hospital systems.\n\nOur solution is practical, easy to use, and very affordable.  Our customers are patients, healthcare professionals and providers, as well as all companies looking to provide added value to their employees through on demand health solutions.\n\nFor patients...Pangianet provides an on-demand answer to your concern\n\nFor doctors..you get enterprise grade tools to better track and diagnose your patients. DICOM for images and media and a complete electronic health record HIPAA compliant and certified by the US National Coordinator of Health Information Technology. No more paying for expensive EHRs. \n\nFor other healthcare professionals,  build your professional profile and generate revenue through professional advice and sales of your products.\n\nAs a hospital communiacate via HL7 standard.  256 bit encryption, save money, say goodbye to paper.\n\nPangianet is the google of health','Anyone Anywhere Anytime Health','[\"Bogota\", \"Earth\", \"Atlanta\", \"Georgia\", \"Colombia\", \"California\", \"North Ameri