n   -  alerts providers/family of sudden changes in symptom severity\n   -  measures treatment efficacy\n   -  identifies potential side-effects\n2. Symple Health empowers patients to share what they learn using Symple App. \n   -  invites users to publish strong symptom/symptom or symptom/factor correlations\n   -  invites users to report by diagnosis\n   -  invites users to add narrative about their findings\n   -  invites viewers to comment, vote or refute\n3. Symple Data is data from consenting users\n   -  data is designed to be searchable by diagnosis, symptom or factor\n   -  empowers pharma to discover post-market side effects\n   -  reveals the patient experience outside the clinical environment\n   -  alerts epidemiologists to emergent events\n','Understand, manage & report symptoms','[\"Princeton\"]','Symple Health'),('Jobinasecond has launched a new SaaS Solution. Introducing SWIFT SHIFT.\n\nSwift Shift is currently changing the way some retailers manage the workforce and reduce labor costs. speaking with retail managers about their day to day. In those discussions, it has become apparent that exceeding contracted hours and shifts lost to absence (upwards of 3%-5% per week) are causing a loss in profit.\n\nWe have developed an Open Shift Management, Regional Staff Bank Creation,and Last Minute Availability tool. The solution leverages a mobile platform which includes SMS, Email, and Push Notifications. This is a completely unique system.\n\nThe benefits include a reduction in overall payroll, a reduction in shifts/hours lost to absence, an increase in transactions, and higher utilization of your current staff. We have a few major UK Retailers trialing our system now.','Last minute availability Tool that significantly reduces labor costs','[\"London\"]','Jobinasecond/ Swift Shift'),('The CloudPhone 3G is a next generation wearable smartphone for healthier, safer, families. \n\nIt keeps seniors & children connected to their family, and delivers powerful insights into their health and wellbeing. We\'re bringing the Quantified Self to family care.\n\nKey points of difference from existing solutions:\n\n- All \'smarts\' are in the cloud. Voice and data are routed through a cloud-platform. \n\n- Voice controlled dialing brings flexibility to 1 button interface. \'Call a taxi\' \'I need help\'  \n\n- Lifestyle Analytics monitors physical activity & relates it to medical info to identify changes in health.\n\n- Automated fall & motion monitoring - asks the wearer \"Are you Ok?\" before causing a fuss.\n\n- Safe Path, a proprietary geolocation system, monitors regular travel like too and from school.\n\n- CloudPhone requires no end user configuration. \n\n- Functionality can be extended to other devices, feature & smartphones via the cloud platform.\n\nSold as a subscription service.','A voice controlled smart care device that monitors health & activity in seniors and kids.','[\"San Francisco\"]','CloudPhone 3G - by ollo mobile'),('Avaz is an iPad/Android app that helps kids with autism and other disabilities develop communication and language capability. Avaz has proven capability to help complement speech therapy and special education. Children use Avaz to select pictures from a vocabulary of 5000+ words, from which Avaz creates a sentence that is spoken out with a natural-sounding voice. Avaz is available in localized versions for USA, Denmark, Australia, India and Italy, with more countries on the way. \n\nAvaz is complemented by a new invention, FreeSpeech. FreeSpeech is a patent-pending, potentially disruptive technology that creates a \'visual grammar\'. ','Speech apps for kids with autism','[\"Chennai\"]','Invention Labs / Avaz'),('SCS Card Technology Inc. has created a patent pending multi-application Personal Health Record smart card – essentially an EHR/EMR on a microprocessor chip that securely carries current and retrospective physician-quality healthcare information. Development and prototype are complete. The platform and suite of proprietary health care-specific applications stand alone in the marketplace, and fulfill all U.S. Meaningful Use requirements. Security is tri-level and includes PIN and biometric functions.\n\nSCS is positioned to advance a game-changing opportunity in an industry stymied by its inability to demonstrate value in the arena of personalized medicine. Our cards and information-matched cloud and terrestrial servers carry a complete health profile, as well as hundreds of pages of segregated clinician and healthcare professionals’ notes. In addition to its medical utility, SCS PHR technology can provide administrative savings up to 30%.\n\n\n','Smart card medical records','[\"Calgary\"]','SCS Card Technology '),('We provide a SaaS clinical practice management system and EHR with smart practice management for the 1.3M mental and behavioral health professionals in the USA. TherapyCharts replaces paper charts, reduces the trend of 20% insurance rejections, and helps assure full current and future HIPAA, legal, and regulatory compliance. Awarded the GLEQ 2010 Best of Biotechnology. One of four semifinalists in the IT category for the Accelerate Michigan 2010 and 2011 competitions.','As SalesForce is to sales, TherapyCharts is to mental health','[\"Ann Arbor\"]','TherapyCharts'),('MedStartr clients are over 20 times more successful than average for healthcare innovation.  This is because we drive massive exposure and let the crowd decide which ideas they like best. MedStartr innovation acceleration and crowdfunding clients succeed over 40% of the time as shown by the 108 partnerships, thousands of new customers, and over $25MM in investments they have garnered after going live on our platform. MedStartr has become the go-to platform to accelerate innovation in healthcare through our campaigns, challenges, and events.that drive press, partnerships, adoption, and funding. We bring together a \"Crowd that Cares\", namely patients, providers, institutions, payers, investors and corporate partners, and create a wave of support, adoption, and investmentlet the crowd show which ideas will be the best investments. We look forward to launching our equity platform in Q1 2014. ','Healthcare Crowd Funding','[\"New York City\"]','MedStartr'),('CareSpeak\'s disease management platform uses 2-way sms-to-web to facilitate real time communication/data exchange between patient & circle-of-care team, leading to improved patient outcomes. \n\nPatients notified via 2way SMS to take medication or measure/report biometrics. If not reported within specified time, escalation alerts sent to caregivers or monitoring service. Patients further engaged via educational and motivational messages. Incentives incorporated via phone allowances & co-pay cards.','Improving patient outcomes via 2way text-to-web mHealth platform','[\"New Jersey\"]','CareSpeak Communications'),('Expat Care software is an expert system that learns the treatment outcomes of treatments and side-effects based on an individual’s combination of genetic mutations and clinical information.It learns how specific treatments affect individuals with particular diseases or conditions due to differences in mutations,weight,age,history,etc.\nExpat Care accounts give an easy way of keeping relevant health information accessible.','Healthcare\'s Cerebral Cortex','[\"Omaha\"]','Expat '),('Startup Incubator portfolio companies benefit from determining the best business model and marketing strategy to commercialize their idea, developing investor proposals in order to get funding and developing significant contact network. \n\nWhat we offer?\nOne-to-one coaching sessions \nAdvice from leading international experts\nAccess to wide network (pool of business angels, venture capitalists)\nNetworking events, workshops, expert panels\nBusiness trips and meetings abroad\n','Tech incubator in Estonia & Prototron Fund','[\"Tallinn\"]','Tehnopol Startup Incubator'),('dF enables new and innovative applications to be developed for the ICU. These applications can help eliminate preventable harms, improve patient outcomes, and increase operational efficiencies in hospitals. dF provides the necessary infrastructure for these applications.','ICU applications platform','[\"Baltimore\"]','dataFASCIA'),('Mugilu helps startups build products. Startups have to work with limited resources and Moogilu steps in and help by adding resources-on-tap. We can not only build products but help startups augment their resources by providing high quality engineers - software, mobile, qa, dba, mathematical modeling, unix sys-admin, windows sys-admin, cloud engineers, 24x7 IT/Application Support. Besides augmentation services, we can build products from concept to delivery to hosting. We have expertise in wide variety of technologies - Java, C/C++, ROR, PHP, MySQL, Oracle, SQLServer, Amazon, GoGrid, Hadoop, Hive, HBase, iPhone, Android, and others. We have technology services including Product Development, Application/Software Development, QA, Data/DBA, IT/Cloud, and 24x7 IT/Application Support.\r\n\r\nWe also have deep expertise in building Healthcare, Financial, Social Media, Marketing, Big Data, and Mobile Apps.','Building Products from Concept to Deployment','[\"Tracy\"]','Mugilu'),('SafeImageMD offers convenient storage and transfer of medical images that is fully HIPAA and DICOM compliant. The four primary services are cloud-based image storage/transfer, fully-functional DICOM viewing, VPN-less integration and web-based image uploading. Our software ensures ability to load and view image data from a wide variety of sources, allowing it to serve as a stand-alone system, or augmentation to an existing image-storing solution.','SaaS medical imaging data solution','[\"Denver\"]','SafeImageMD'),('Hello Doctor™ enables you to control your health. By managing medical records from multiple sources, we provide you easy real-time access to all the information you need in order to understand your medical condition.\n\nNow available in the App Store: www.hello.do/d/al','Medical records organizer','[\"Palo Alto\"]','Hello Doctor'),('MedPath Solutions Inc. is an early stage medical software company that will implement a workflow standard for formatting surgical pathology reports while securely storing clinical data and transforming this data in to information driving knowledge in to understanding.  The current pathology laboratory systems (LIS) provide the basic benefits of a pathology workflow, but few of them excel in specialized decision support capabilities.  Our SaaS platform is a comprehensive pathology platform designed to alleviate the daily laboratory workflow challenges by maximizing the future advancements in pathology.  These advancements include standardized specimen handling and processing techniques, streamline data entry processes to reduce human error and the re-use of clinical data that is captured during the normal diagnostic workflow.','SaaS for Pathology','[\"Buffalo\"]','MedPath Solutions '),('JumperCut helps health care providers engage their patients with rich media and data collection that meets the digital and social consumer where they are.  And we do it with a philosophy of simplifying the consumer and provider health care experience.  Our embeddable interactive patient interface, compatible across all web and mobile platforms, engages patients by blending interactive survey technology with highly personalized video education content, collecting patient outcomes and driving meaningful, long-term impact.  Our physician dashboard makes it easy to select specific video education sequences for patients related to their unique needs and their visit, prescribe post-visit followup surveys, and view reports on system usage and patient outcomes.  ','JumperCut is Personalized Patient Enagagement','[\"Portland\"]','JumperCut'),('Read by QxMD is a personalized medical/scientific journal for iPad, iPhone and web.   Physicians and scientists use it to keep up with new research, read outstanding topic reviews and search PubMed.  It\'s like Flipboard for healthcare.\n\nHospitals, governments, insurers, and industry partners pay to use the platform to disseminate knowledge and change practice at the point of care.','Flipboard meets PubMed http://qx.md/read','[\"Vancouver\"]','QxMD'),('Surgerica provides cost and quality transparency through a health care management suite that delivers proven, measurable results for patients. By providing credible, relevant, and precise cost and quality information, Surgerica has helped hundreds of thousands of people, become smarter about how they find and utilize health care.\nA patient can also opt for a Video Consultation with Top Doctors & the last but the best feature is that he can connect with other people who had same treatment in same hospital where he is planning to go. It\'s an ecosystem comprising all stakeholders--doctors, hospitals, and patients--and you can determine exactly how much a treatment would cost before you approach healthcare providers.','Trip-Advisor for Healthcare Services ..Bringing Transparency to Healthcare','[\"Calcutta\"]','Surgerica'),('Paduin improves your health with food and lifestyle coaching. The app gets to know you, then, bit by bit, it changes your eating and lifestyle habits. It\'s a nutritionist in your phone.','A nutritionist in your phone.','[\"Fredericton\"]','Paduin'),('We create on-line platform for performing various neurocognitive tasks. The most powerful product is on-drug addict detection through simple audiovisual testing. The tests can be disguised in games or other software.\n\nAnother product based on the same technology is on-line tool for early  stroke risk prediction.\n\nWe also consider creating products for dealing with stress, depression, exhaustion, talents, etc.\n\nWe strive to make computer to \'feel\' the user. All tests are non-verbal.','Remote brain tests that substitute substance tests (drug abuse, etc.)','[\"Riga\"]','Braintest'),('Modest Tree is creating a suite of innovative 3D authoring applications for the rapid development of highly interactive 3D training scenarios.\n\n','3D training solutions','[\"Halifax\"]','Modest Tree Media'),('rehab|neXt connects patients with therapists to measure progress and customize their care plan and store it in a central location that can be accessed from anywhere.','A fun and interactive continuity of care software solution for rehabilitative treatment.','[\"Buffalo\"]','rehab|neXt'),('Kinergy Health has developed an award-winning, HIPAA-compliant, patient-centered technology + care navigation service, resulting in effective scalable care coordination across health care settings. Kinergy\'s tech connects hospitals, home health agencies, primary care offices, etc. to each other and to the patient/caregiver, resulting in improved communications, the elimination of care transition \"dropped balls\" and reduced hospital readmissions.\n\nInadequate care coordination is a $25+BN problem. Hospitals are increasingly \"on the hook\" financially for patients\' recovery, but do not have visibility post-discharge into the home or another facility. Home health agencies & family caregivers have visibility, but are not connected to the hospital. Kinergy provides a common platform so all care team members can be connected, communicate with each other and share information.  Kinergy sells direct to hospitals and via relationships with home health agencies utilizing Kinergy\'s tech.\n','Simplified care management with technology + care navigator model','[]','Kinergy Health'),('What is IceDreamApp?\nIceDreamApp is the first and only social dream network where users can share their sleeping dreams in our dream feed within the app where they can interact with other people by commenting and liking their friends dreams.  Users can opt to post their dreams from our own social network to other social networks like Twitter or Facebook.  Users can also keep their dreams private and use the app as their own personal dream diary.  The app also features a monthly calendar that shows users how often they are dreaming and how often they are having good dreams versus bad dreams.\n\n.................................................\niTunes\nitunes.apple.com/ar/app/icedreamapp/id634681287?mt=8\nEmail:\nicedreamapp@gmail.com\nWebsite: \nicedreamapp.com\nFacebook: \nhttps://www.facebook.com/IceDreamApp\nTwitter:\nhttp://www.twitter.com/icedreamapp\nInstagram\nIceDreamApp\nYoutube Channel\nhttps://www.youtube.com/user/iceDreamApp?feature=watch','Social dream journal for iPhone','[\"New York City\"]','IceDreamApp'),('We want to build the next generation search engine that can search the unGoogled world via an open machine learning platform. Google only searches 2% of the information out there so who searches the 98%? We have developed the core engine that can quickly look at unstructured information and algorithmically understand and display those hidden relationships. Moreover, HITCH is clever enough to be able to generate a rich taxonomy even if those words are not mentioned in the descriptions. We are currently building a crowd sourcing interface where users (hundreds, thousands or millions) can make it better and smarter. This optimizes the machine learning, natural language process and the human element to make it an incredibly powerful service. It\'s like the Wordpress model where we provide the platform and let companies build on the HiTCH engine to help them structure their unstructured information. In short, we let a million HiTCH powered engines bloom.','structuring the world\'s information','[\"New York City\"]','HiTCH'),('Rera is a real-time platform that provides healthcare professionals with immediate feedback on time-sensitive questions from a broad network of qualified specialists.','Quora + Twitter for the Emergency Room','[\"Dallas\"]','Rera Health'),('Nearly 70% of American adults are overweight or obese and more than 20% of children ageing between 6-19 years face the same issue. Research shows overweight kids have bad self image and lower performance in school, while busy parents list lack of knowledge and motivation as top reasons for not changing their eating habits.\n\nCoachingWill is an on-line solution to help overweight families start leading a healthy lifestyle. It gives parents a set of tools to prepare easy, fast and healthy meals and it uses gamification to motivate the kids to follow the plan. \n\nIt\'s hard to change bad habits, but it\'s never too late. CoachingWill helps by making it fun and rewarding!\n','Raising healthy eaters','[\"London\"]','CoachingWill'),('Handle My Health are the creators of MIAMI - the patient intelligence platform based on smartphones and the web. Supporting patients from discovery through to recovery, by empowering patients through health literacy, improving medicines management and personalised care through big data analytics and intelligence reporting. Reducing the impact of illness, by helping users receive personalised care, enhancing reporting channels and analysing large personal health datasets to determine risk of complications, helping to personalise care and reduce hospital re/admission rates.\n\nCurrently pilots are active in mental health and oncology in the UK.','Reclaim your health! mHealth big data patient intelligence platform','[\"London\"]','Handle My Health'),('Flextracker have 3 main targets: \n1 – Process Medical Data gathered from Eletronic Medical Records, Genetic Data, Mobile Apps, Public Dataset, Sensors, Medical Images and Emotional Data.\n2 – Through the “Remote Support” to patients, analyze your data and give advices or invitations to medical clinic to execute a preventive procedure.\n3 – Create a Market Place to Medical data, thus helping to dissolve the users barrier to share your personal data getting money to users for your shared data.\n','Platform to Preventive Medicine','[\"Santiago\"]','Flextracker'),('Smarter, simpler, connected patient education.  Centrana (formerly Uprise) is a SaaS and mobile platform to access, manage, and prescribe multimedia patient education content and track patient engagement across the continuum of care.  Our learning and content management system unifies the sources of multimedia patient education content and makes it simple for providers to consistently delivery high-quality, evidence-based materials to patients.\n','Learning and content management system for patient education','[\"Cambridge, MA\"]','Centrana Health'),('We provide extremely hi-quality Wearable Electronics mainly for Health Care and Consumers.\n\nWe\'re also working to bring smart devices to your wrist and neck. Think of the Pebble Watch but useable by every device, Phones to Tablets and Desktops making our product for EVERYONE and designed to be for the Medical Industry.','Wearable Health for Emergency, Self-Diagnosing, & Cloud Services','[\"Las Vegas\"]','Wearing Digital'),('Beneufit is a personalized exercise platform for people with major neurological disorders, tapping into the brain’s natural ability to heal itself. Our patent-pending technology combines exercise, mobile devices, wireless sensors and big data with the goal of minimizing the condition’s impact on patients, reducing the costs to society and advancing the understanding of exercise’s impact on the brain.\n\nOur first targeted condition is Parkinson\'s disease, others include stroke rehabilitation, traumatic brain injury and dementia.\n\nRevenue will come from fitness sensor sales and monthly subscriptions to the personalized workouts and caregiver dashboard.','Exercise as Medicine','[\"San Francisco\"]','Beneufit'),(NULL,'A mentor-centric accelerator for health-centric startups','[\"Louisville\"]','XLerateHealth'),('PRX Control Solutions is a company specialized in developing apps for prescription control and health management. \n\nRight now we have 2 apps and launching a third one in mid-2.014: \n\n- PCA Audit: is an app used to audit and process health claims with pharmaceutical treatments. This app guarantees our customers with millions of dollars in savings by detecting fraud and controlling and supervising patients with their intake of chronic and acute medications. \n- PCA Farma: This app helps pharmacies increase their sales by controlling and supervising chronic patients. How does it work? Pharmacies register the patient’s prescription data in the app and we do the rest. We call patients to see how they’re doing with their treatments and we send them reminders so they can retrieve their prescriptions in our customer’s stores.\n- PCA Metrics: PCA Metrics is and app that offers real time health analytics from real clinical cases provided by our other 2 apps. Ready in mid-2.014. \n','Apps for prescription control and health management','[\"Caracas\"]','PRX Control Solutions'),('GoodMomming is an intelligent platform that assists moms with early parenting decisions by providing personalized recommendations. \n\nBy leveraging technology and algorithms, we assist parents take the best decisions depending on their unique babies’ requirements. \n\nThe results will consist in more confident and happy parents and less money spent on expensive books and useless visits to the pediatrician.','Personalized baby feeding recommendations for new parents. ','[\"London\"]','Good Momming!'),('KINESIO radically shifts physical therapy monitoring & measurements into the 21st century, dramatically impacting the lives of patients.','Measure. Monitor. Make A Difference','[\"Dallas\"]','Kinesio'),('AccessMyDoc is a web based HIPAA compliant virtual office medical clinic that increases access to primary care physicians and specialist by allowing patients to receive medical care for non-life threatening illnesses in real-time from their home, worksite or the emergency room. “AccessMyDoc.com is a web-based solution that allows patients to receive real-time medical care via a secured web based application” \nCustomers for our product are rural and semi-urban population.','Virtual Tele Hospitals','[\"Hyderabad\"]','INSTA Intelligence Technologies'),('Proven Electronic Medical Records and EDI Revenue Management for Psychiatry, Mental Health;  Nursing Homes, Extended care Homes, Elderly care homes and Rehabilitation centers. Demand for our product will increase tremendously within the next two years due to the mandates specified in the Affordable Care Act requiring electronic medical records by 2014, and with the increasing age of the Baby Boomer Generation.\n','Electronic Medical Records for Mental Health','[\"Miami\"]','PatientTrac '),('Intraclinics allows physicians to communicate securely anytime, anywhere. Our technology leverages the hardware found in pockets across the world, the smartphone. Physicians login to their Iphone, Android, or Web dashboard and begin communicating. Within our platform they can refer to specialists with the touch of a finger, follow-up with consults anytime, anywhere, and print out a concise wrap-up of the days conversations. Intraclinics removes the barriers from communicating while remaining absolutely secure.','Secure Communications for Physicians.','[\"Cleveland\"]','Intraclinics'),('It started with a simple question: \"What do you know about your great-grandfather?\" To which our newly-minted teen quickly quipped: \"He was REALLY rich.\" Horrified, his NaNa chided us for relaying so little of her father\'s legacy and that she wished she had some way of keeping his words of wisdom fresh for future generations. \n\nThe problem? \n\nThere were too many clunky and cluttered websites. What she needed was an intuitive online toolkit that was simple to navigate, record and replay key moments in life when it mattered most. \n\nChronicling facts and translating them into simple stories are an obsession of ours. The problem WisdomBox solves speaks to its purpose of creating an online legacy toolkit for those affected by life-threatening illnesses. WisdomBox is a place to capture, store and share your legacy, and the wisdom of a life well-lived, with those you love and with the world.\n\nDefine what you leave behind.\n\nWisdomBox.me','Define what you leave behind. An online legacy toolkit for those affected by illnesses.','[\"San Francisco\"]','WisdomBox'),('CareSolver is a simple, safe, & comprehensive care management platform for the 43M informal family caregivers providing 83% of senior care in the US. CareSolver delivers dynamic, customized task-based careplans covering the clinical & non-clinical aspects of providing care to an aging parent alongside content, vendor services, & collaboration tools necessary to complete tasks successfully. CareSolver increases care quality while decreasing caregiver burden.','A care management platform for family caregivers providing care to aging loved ones','[\"Boston\"]','CareSolver'),(' AEGLE Life™. Where health, mobile tech and big data meet.\n\nStaying healthy is a challenge to most of us. AEGLE Life™ provides a smart, personalised health and wellness platform collating and analysing data from mobile enabled devices, which combined with self-assessments and scientific evidence, provide insights that help individuals make better lifestyle choices. AEGLE Work™ also provides aggregated insights that help companies validate their health initiatives.\n \nWe plan our initial pilot with a major employer in early 2014. The pilot will validate outcomes related to mental wellbeing and men’s health. The capabilities will be packaged into the AEGLE Work™ product, which will be sold to employers starting with the resources industry. Longer term, the platform will also collect data and provide correlations between environmental factors and human telemetry, a big data play of interest to public policy and technology developers.','Personalised, data-driven health, prevention and wellness','[\"Perth\"]','AEGLE Life'),('Project Management Software , for Clinical Procedures ( Hip Operations , Cardiac Pacing etc).\r\nHelps Standarise Treatment , Smooth the Patient Flow , and deliver Clinical Metrics to establish Benchmarks and optimse Efficiency , improving safety and cost effectiveness.','UX meets RX ( \'BaseCamp\' for Hospitals)','[\"London\"]','AIRO'),('With the advent of complete genome sequencing systems, the need arises to process large amounts of data in a systematic and routinely manner. Robust databases exist which can store DNA data. The real challenge is to DO something with the data, such that people benefit (health wise).\nGenAlice is a unique high performance database extension, which enables large scale correlation of large and complex combined datasets (DNA-, diagnostic-, pathway- and treatment expectation/response- data).','Groundbreaking technology in the field of DNA research','[\"Netherlands\"]','Genalice B.V.'),('Yorn is a real-time feedback platform for healthcare settings. Optimized for mobile, Yorn’s “Feedback as a Service” (FaaS™) enables patients and participants to provide feedback, in the moment, on any healthcare experience. \n\nProviders and payers can identify root causes of issues and make appropriate operational changes that improve patient experience and satisfaction. Yorn delivers clinical and economic benefit that can correlate to higher quality ratings on performance.\n','','[\"Philadelphia\"]','Yorn'),('CrystalMD creates web utilities at the intersection of mobile and social for HealthCare providers to increase patient flow and drive efficiency in care delivery by 20% or more. \n\nCrystalMD platform includes features that increase patient satisfaction while tangibly impacting the practice bottomline. Reach out to us to learn more about how doctors are using the CrystalMD platform with features such as:\n\nCrystalSite™ \nCrystalAnalytics™ \nCrystalText™ \nCrystalReviews™ \nCrystalSocial™\nCrystalCompliance™\n ','SinglePlatform for Healthcare  ','[\"New York City\"]','CrystalMD'),('In an emergency, the N-1-1 mobile app lets people alert nearby off duty EMTs, medical personnel, and other responders who also have the N-1-1 app so that they can quickly come to provide aid. \r\n\r\nSpeed is a factor when dealing with emergencies.  75% of sudden cardiac arrest victims do not receive bystander CPR. 529,000 women die every year from unassisted childbirth.  The first 48 hours after a missing person disappears is the best window for recovering them\r\n\r\nAt any given moment dispatch centers all over the world have 3-4 times as many people off-duty and roaming around than they have on-duty at the station.  Additionally, most countries have large number of everyday citizens who may be near an emergency and able to help, but who never even get the call.  N-1-1 crowdsources emergency response to lets anyone tap into it’s emergency network to quickly get or give aid.','Crowdsourcing Emergency Response ','[\"Vienna, VA\"]','N-1-1'),('SynerMed has launched SynerMed Incubator.  Come work with us to launch the next healthcare innovation that will reduce cost, improve quality and improve customer satisfaction.  \r\n\r\nWe offer funding and administrative and IT support.\r\n\r\nWe have an ecosystem of 10,000 physicians; 750,000 patients; and $500,000,000 of healthcare spend.','innovating healthcare through a connected platform','[\"Monterey Park\"]','SynerMed '),('A systematic approach to building great businessdrawn from world-class innovation.','University Commercialisation Done Right','[\"Melbourne\"]','Nest Group Limited'),('Draagle.com is the most advanced full scale semantic web of drug information. It\'s useful tool for medical profesionals as well as for concerned patients. It offers the most precise  advertising for drugs and supplements.','Semantic web of drug information','[\"Ljubljana\"]','Draagle'),('SchedFull wants to revolutionize the scheduling experience to make it patient centric so that patients can get appointments when they need it. We accomplish this by automating scheduling workflow and helping to remind, reschedule, and fill cancellations so our clients can focus on caring for patients.  SchedFull aims to provide its services to a variety of healthcare professionals across physician offices, clinics, hospitals, radiology practices, and dentistry offices. ','Cancellation Management Scheduling Software','[\"Fremont\"]','SchedFull'),('Cientis facilitates the adoption and use of health information technology to reduce the cost of care and improve healthcare delivery. Our online communities provide the largest and most comprehensive Health IT satisfaction rating data available in North America. \n\nCientis has partnerships with 21 Medical Societies representing over 720,000 licensed physicians (over 75% of the market) in the United States. Our core revenue is derived from research, consulting and sponsorships.','Health IT Social Network','[\"Vancouver\"]','Cientis Technologies'),('PrescribeWellness was founded in 2010 with a mission of reducing health care costs and improving health in America. Our Automated Digital Intervention (ADI) system delivers cloud-based communications and facilitates collaboration of health care providers, family and other stakeholders to improve care and outcomes. Some of our services include population health, medication adherence, chronic disease management, behavioral change programs and transitional care','Cloud-Based Technology for Health Care Communication','[\"Laguna Beach\"]','Prescribe Wellness'),('CareTrio makes it easy to bring together family, friends, and caregivers\nto help manage your loved one\'s health. Coordinate care for a sick sibling, disabled child, or aging parent no matter where they are, how many family members are involved, or how complex their needs are. We securely store all of your important information about your loved one - news, photos, stories, medical records, medications, appointments, and more - in one place, accessible from anywhere in the world, on any device.\n\n','Secure family caregiving','[\"Seattle\"]','CareTrio'),('dVisit is a platform that allows existing patients to save time (2.5 hr on avg) & be treated by their family doctor for routine illnesses and for the doctor to get paid for that care & maintain Continuity of Care for patients while managing patient volume.','Uber for Patient Visits','[\"Nashville\"]','dVisit'),('E Mental Health Center offers Second Generation Telehealth Web Application Platforms whose functionalities keep First Generation Supports while adding Health Plan\'s wanted features such as: \n\n- Outcome and Quality Assessments.\n\n- Support Systems for Clients/Patients that boost recovery.\n\n- Support Systems for Providers that increase their effectiveness.\n\n- True Cost Containment via the potential for developing automated Pay Per Performance fee schedules.\n\n','Second Generation Telehealth Web Application Platforms','[\"Los Angeles\"]','E Mental Health Center'),('TeleSkin makes hardware, software, and mobile solutions for the early diagnosis of skin cancer, skin health, and other dermatological conditions.  skinScan is our Windows 8 mobile and tablet, Healthvault connected, application for patients and consumers to analyze their skin and connect with doctors for expert opinions. skinScan integrates seamlessly with our integrated hardware/software solution which includes a clinical multi-spectral dermascope for detailed dermascopic skin analysis.','Mobile and clinical skin cancer analysis','[\"Belgrade\"]','TeleSkin'),('CoRehab product is physically composed by a mini-pc with therapeutic videogames on it, a set of wearable motion sensing controller coupled with a pressure platform and a web application. CoRehab designs the hardware components and develops the whole software and the web\napplication. Through the web application, the physiotherapist controls his patients and set personalized exercizes and parameters for each one. Parameters and results are saved on a centralized database. ','Therapeutic gaming for home-based rehabilitation with asynchronous control of doctors','[\"Trento\"]','CoRehab'),('Med-room helps you promptly find a doctor or a medical service and conveniently book a doctor\'s appointment online.\n','A web medical registry targeted at the Russian market.','[\"Novosibirsk\"]','\"Med-Room\"'),('Eating too much salt is one of the top 3 ways that heart failure patients return to the hospital within 30 days of discharge.\n\nSounds simple, right?\n\nAccording to the AHA, nearly a quarter of heart failure patients are readmitted within 30 days, and over half are readmitted in 6 months.\n\nMaybe not so simple?\n\nWeHealth translates theoretical dietary recommendations into practical advice on what patients should eat everyday to best manage their chronic diseases. WeHealth does this by using a food grading system based on a proprietary data set. \n\nWe’ve derived algorithms to transform millions of data points into clear dietary guidelines.  Simply put, our software gives patients personalized eating advice: for W chronic disease,  eat X amount of Y foods and avoid Z others to best protect health and happiness.\n\nWeHealth will bridge the knowledge gap, and provide the detailed dietary info that many people have limited access to, or just don\'t know how to properly interpret. ','Tech Empowerment for Chronic Disease Management','[\"Santiago\"]','WE Health'),('LifeVest is the “stock” for your health.\n\nLifeVest addresses the $6 billion problem in workplace wellness, return on investment (ROI). Through a “stock” tied to each employee’s health, our progress-based program ties health incentives dollars directly to reduction in health risk.\n\nWe transform the abstract value of better health into something concrete and desirable, cash.\n\nIn a simple to use, fun and highly engaging platform modeled after the stock market, our users are motivated to track their health and their earnings daily.\n\nLifeVest is fundamentally changing the way we see health by changing the way we value it.\n','The \"stock\" tied to your health','[\"Princeton\"]','LifeVest Health'),('Infonaut’s Hospital Watch Live (HWL) is a healthcare IT & surveillance solution that helps control and stop hospital infections.\r\n\r\nOur solution enables:\r\n\r\n• Hand hygiene compliance for staff AND patients.\r\n• Detect infection hotspots to identify reservoirs of disease\r\n• Pattern recognition: ID ‘emerging practices’ to create the new Gold Standards\r\n• Track environmental cleaning to ensure equipment & rooms are properly disinfected\r\n• Outbreak management: Gives you the ability to quickly track, contain & control. \r\n• Automated contact tracing: Risk-rated, accurate & instant\r\n• Occupational safety: Immediately alert clinicians & staff upon their exposure.\r\n\r\nOutcomes we enable include:\r\n- Reduced Infection Rates\r\n- Increased Hand Hygiene Compliance\r\n- Reduced Readmissions\r\n- Reduced LOS\r\n- Increased Throughput\r\n\r\nWe grew from the SARS crisis and are recognized internationally for our work in disease surveillance.','Healthcare BI to control and stop hospital acquired infections','[\"Toronto\"]','Infonaut'),('ClickMedix enables delivery of high-quality, comprehensive healthcare when and where care is needed through its patent-pending mobile health and education (MHE) system sold to physicians and health organizations as software-as-a-service. A single \"ClickMedix\" mobile application installed on a phone or tablet, or accessed through a web browser, creates a “One-Click” experience for health providers desiring to serve more patients and for patients seeking effective care. \n\nClickMedix has been used in 13 countries, including US, China, and India, with published success in expediting time to treatment for patients, and creating new jobs supplementing the shortage of medical personnel, while reducing overall costs of delivering healthcare.\nDocumented uses of ClickMedix include: \n•	Specialist consultation \n•	Chronic disease management (diabetes, hypertension, etc.)\n•	Home-visit care for seniors \n•	Remote training and care coordination \n•	Real-time data analysis for public health interventions','One-Click-Healthcare mHealth Commerce Platform','[\"Rockville\"]','ClickMedix'),('Duet Health, is a platform for patient education, engagement, & motivation-based behavior change in specialties such as OB/GYN, Orthopedics, Cardiology, Endocrinology, & more.','Mobile Patient Education Platform','[\"Columbus\"]','Duet Health'),('HIT Consultant is an award winning healthcare technology editorial news site that provides deep insights and analysis of healthcare technology trends and innovation. \n\nWe utilize a combination of content from our talented editorial team, quality content curation and thought leading contributors serving as the leading digital media news outlet to connect and engage healthcare technology professionals.\n\nHIT Consultant Media also assists healthcare technology companies in content strategy and development services. \n\n\n','Insightful digital media coverage of healthcare innovation','[\"Atlanta\"]','HIT Consultant Media'),('We offer a deep analysis of a couples\' 23andMe genetic data to help them understand the risks and benefits that they may pass on to their children.  We\'ll show them the best and worst traits that they\'ll pass on to their kids, as well as the traits that they\'ll certainly pass on, and the traits that they could possibly change.  Our analysis is free and available within minutes.','Healthier families through genetics','[\"New York City\"]','Genes and Us'),('Rehapp is a is cloud based rehabilitation platform integrated with IPad App games for children with mental disabilities and a web page community that let\'s parents track their children\'s progress metrics and connect to other parents and therapists.','Tailored rehabilitation for loving families. ','[\"Santiago\"]','REHAPP'),('i-NOTZ solves the problem of modernising medicine with its fast and intuitive-front-end, just ‘touch-to-type’, no keyboard, no dictation. Ideal for tablets, \'think-ahead\' logic converts screen taps to fluent text. It saves hours each week eliminating the dreaded task of dictation. The digital depth gives the opportunity for additional innovative revenue streams. i-NOTZ can be integrated or stand-alone so partnering is profitable and productive.','disruptive technology addressing $50 billion legacy market','[\"London\"]','OnICS Limited'),('Our core focus is on Healthcare IT and at present we are working on our Bluetooth ECG Device which is a big landmark as it will revolutionize the old out dated and out fashioned ECG Monitoring system and will enable healthcare providers to get ECG through Laptops and Smartphones. \n\nWe are going to integrate our solution with OpenEMR so that healthcare practitioners could access their record remotely through web interface. We will also offer our SDK to outside researchers for research purposes.\n\nOther than this we have already completed our flagship Enterprise Management solution and offering it to enterprises. This solution is aimed at providing Systems Management Service to Enterprises to help them minimize IT risks. It is a single console based Grid Control and when installed on a Customer PC in the form of Monitoring Agent, it will help us to monitor the systems of the customer at a remote place and will enable us to keep our customers safe from potential IT threats.','Smartphone Healthcare','[\"Bahawalpur\"]','VisioTech Solutions'),('Qi Text uses diagnosis-specific configurable mobile messaging to improve communication between providers and patients beyond the point of care. An example would be setting an automatic message to remind a patient to take her prescription drug at a certain time of day.  Another example would be to text a patient early in the morning the day of a bloodwork appointment to remind him not to eat.  [Qi is Chinese 