t drive poor outcomes and high costs in these patients. Moreover, the platform allows care coordinators to successfully achieve these goals while minimizing disruptions to physician workflows.','Platform for Team-based Care','[\"San Francisco\"]','Acupera'),('Beyond its ability to present raw data in an easy-to-interpret fashion, the dental dashboard also integrates social media capabilities and advice from industry experts. This allows doctors to share information and best practices, ask and respond to business questions posted by fellow members, consult a library of video training, and facilitate access to subject matter experts for problem resolution.','praccel.com','[\"Cleveland\"]','dental dashboard'),('Wave\'s mobile app allows epileptics to use their Smartphones paired wirelessly with a peripheral device and wearable sensors as an ambulatory EEG solution for the remote monitoring of epileptics. The app is downloaded free (e.g. Android, iOS, Blackberry) the peripheral and sensors purchased/rented through the app. Our services are fully reimbursable by payer groups at rate of approximately $750/day for each patient. ','Ambulatory EEG Mobile App','[\"Chicago\", \"San Diego\"]','Wave Technology Group'),('A patient-to-medication pairing solution based upon correlating scientific trials, crowd sourced data, and lab gas chromatography of medical cannabis. The resultant analysis provides a rating scale for ailments such as pain relief, sleep aid, and more. \n\nBudGenius.com serves as an unofficial \"Physician\'s Desk Reference\" for medical cannabis, and looks forward to advancing our technology to begin matching the most effective strains to critical conditions such as Alzheimers, Parkinsons, Cancer. \n','Crowdsourcing patient data for determining alternative medicine efficacy','[\"Los Angeles\"]','BudGenius'),('We provide an easy to use, hassle-free web app (Software as a Service or SaaS) for reporting, logging and evaluating Adverse Events (an adverse event, AE for short, is any undesirable experience associated with the medical treatment of a patient) in Healthcare, creating an instance to successfully apply countermeasures to avoid future related AEs.\r\n\r\nStandardizes the process of reporting, logging and evaluatiang AEs across medical facilities (public and private) Country-wide.\r\n\r\nRevamps the current process of AE reporting (underused,undermanaged) User oriented plataform to increase report engagement.\r\n\r\n','Adverse Events Webapp for Healthcare','[\"Chile\"]','Sirias'),('The first of its kind virtual exchange/clearinghouse for buyers and sellers of perishable biologics and pharmaceuticals.\n\nThink: Amazon.com/CME/Bloomberg.\n\nInitial products are human blood products; $6 billion+ of blood products are sold each year, the largest pharmaceuticals in the United States.\n\nData collection (big data) and transaction execution services will optimize the blood collection and utilization efforts for the entire country and establish an export market.\n','Clearinghouse & Exchange for perishable biologics and pharmaceuticals','[\"Minneapolis\"]','General Blood'),('We are building a private digital health profile with one-on-one doctor/patient communications. Our secure, HIPAA compliant platform enables physicians to offer remote, direct access to their own patients through a mobile/online lightweight EHR with embedded messaging (text and images) and video chat. We plan to transform the revenue model for providers from traditional fee-for-service billing onto a recurring revenue model that provides incentive for offering enhanced levels of patient access.','Connecting patients with their own doctors via video chat and messaging','[\"Denver\"]','CirrusMD'),('fliiTherapy is a platform for healthcare providers to help patients improve recovery outcomes after injury. Our web and mobile app simplifies the rehab program development process and empowers patients to take control of their recovery. Patient compliance helps reduce the likelihood of readmission and creates additional capacity for therapists to generate more revenue. Our proprietary algorithm tracks and analyzes patient logs and outcome data to support evidence-based decision-making.','Personalized Rehab Program Development and Remote Patient Management','[\"Toronto\"]','fliiTherapy'),('http://labs.developingsmart.org\n\nWe are an app development shop for early stage or resource-strapped social enterprises, charities, and non-profits that need software solutions to serve a core function of their operations.  We find talented students who are interested in creating sustainable solutions to real world problems.  We provide these students with mentorship and opportunities to execute on problems that are too expensive for various organizations to solve.  Students provide their creativity as well as skills in the creation of these solutions.  We are currently growing our pipeline of products and looking for more people as well.  Feel free to reach out to us at smartlabs@developingsmart.org\n\nPast Projects:\n- Created a mobile telemedicine application for a network of medical clinics located in rural Thailand.  ','Bridging the gap between student skills and needs of social organizations','[\"Toronto\"]','SmartLabs'),('MediCard is a patient searching service for medical organizations which take part in clinical trials Our internet-service helps medical organizations, universities and hospitals to find easily and fast patients for clinical trials at any stage. We find patients from online-marketing (SMM, forums, Google.Analytics etc.). Also we cooperate with hospitals and doctors, who recommend their patients our service.','Clinical trials patient searching engine','[\"Moscow\"]','MediCard'),('We help retail and ecommerce businesses build APIs so that they can sell their products on online marketplaces like Magento, Amazon, eBay, osCommerce.\n\nAn API which stands for Application Programming Interface, is a way to let businesses sell their products outside of their core ecommerce site. Except they take a lot technical expertise to build and manage and can get expensive very quickly.\n\nPliant Labs allows businesses to build APIs with an easy use tools and then publish their product data to marketplaces in 3 easy steps.\n\nWe then manage it for them. Its free to use and businesses only pay when they sell products or the APIs get accessed by marketplaces or developers.','We enable businesses to create, publish & use APIs to sell more of everything, anywhere.','[\"Atlanta\"]','Pliant Labs'),('Teamscope is an app that lets medical professionals team up and gather research data together with their colleagues, right from their own mobile devices.','Crowdsourcing medical research','[\"Santiago\"]','Teamscope'),('Providing an efficient and integrated healthcare platform','Integrated Health Systems','[\"Santiago\"]','Inhesy'),('Our first publicly available product is our winning entry into HHS\' Now Trending Challenge: MappyHealth. MappyHealth mines twitter data looking for health term trends. We are working with the US federal government and other agencies to improve our system and make it available for the people who need it most.\n\nWe are working on a consumer-facing health system too. ','Building platforms that positively impact health','[\"Fishers\"]','Social Health Insights'),('ProHEALTH.\n\nDesigned specifically for remote care providers in the field, ProHEALTH is accessible anytime and anywhere enabling care providers to instantly access scheduling, manage patient records, and input patient paperwork right from the point-of-care, while ensuring care firms have real-time communication, coordination, and transparency with their remote workforce. ','Mobile Healthcare Records','[\"Toronto\"]','Professional Performance'),('Adherial’s software allows corporations and their benefit brokers to develop and continuously improve fine-grained, accurately targeted wellness programs and interventions. We tie plan management and patient apps through secure mobile communications, reminders, member responses and communication with plan managers and healthcare providers.\r\nAdherial integrates existing patient data with mobile communication capabilities and secure user management. Key elements of the platform include:\r\n•	Automated member profile with member plan data, historical billing data, and eventually content from the member’s electronic health record.\r\n•	Secure user account creation and synching with member profile.\r\n•	Two-way, multi-modal communication, including messaging and reminders to members based on automated or manual configuration.\r\n•	Support for escalation to social and clinical networks.\r\n•	Administrative dashboards for setting automated communication protocols and for designing custom messaging.','Improving health & reducing healthcare costs in company Health & Wellness programs. ','[\"Portland\"]','Adherial'),('Umbie Office is the leading all-in-one practice management solution for small to medium sized dental clinics; it\'s the best way to apply healthcare information technology to your practice. Imagine having the freedom to access your practice\'s information from anywhere; check schedules and finish up notes from your home, or even review charts while on the road.','Practice Management in the Cloud','[\"Connecticut\"]','Umbie Office'),('GroupMD is a patient-centered collaboration platform that connects care teams across all the organizations where a patient receives care.  GroupMD creates a \"hub and spoke\" network, where the patient is at the center of their care team, where information flows freely, where data can be leveraged and where care becomes proactive.\n\n','Secure place where care teams share information, collaborate and coordinate patient care','[\"San Francisco\"]','GroupMD'),('Our Ovulona™ Smart Sensor’s first application will tell the woman FERTILE DAY 1, 2 and 3 = OVULATION. Another indication will read: PREGNANCY DETECTED. Yet another: SEE DOCTOR ABOUT CERVIX.\n\nOur monitor overcomes the failure of current products and methods to precisely report the fertile window, truly optimizing the probability of conception. \n\nOur monitor’s accuracy also allows for pregnancy avoidance. \n\nMonitoring the cervix means built-in instant pregnancy detection, and prospectively an unobtrusive innocuous cervical health screen. \n\nWe proved the concept and secured FDA clearance. Now we\'ll present the concept to the market. See http://biozhena.files.wordpress.com/2013/11/tweetroducing-biozhena-in-8-slides-e.pps. \n\nLearn more about Transforming Female Reproductive Health Management in narrated slideshow http://biozhena.files.wordpress.com/2013/11/10_biozhena_selected_narrated_slides_102813e-5.pps\n\nThe above video clip \"Fertility, ovulation sensor\" is from the early prototype era.','Diagnostic technology platform introduced via FDA-cleared women\'s fertility breakthrough ','[\"Fort Collins\"]','bioZhena Corporation'),('Building a community of digital health innovators. With over 250 members and 10+ startups we are supporting Madison as a hub of health tech innovation.','','[\"Madison\"]','Madison Health Tech'),('We\'re building a SAAS EMR for Canadian physicians. Its completely web-based and takes only minutes to set up without having to purchase costly servers or extra hardware. Best of all, no set-up fees.\n\nWe\'re taking the hassle out of EMR for Canadian docs. \n\nOur software is a complete practice management solution including full charting, scheduling and billing capabilities.','SAAS Electronic Medical Records for Canada','[\"Victoria\"]','Cloud Practice'),('Kurbi is a Care-Team Coordination platform for chronic disease communities. Our web and mobile applications make it easy for patients to track their health and collaborate with their family and care-providers to get questions answered. Our core users are those that are currently using paper based journals to keep track of their symptoms, diet, and exercises. Kurbi makes it easier to keep track of this data and share it with family and doctors.\n\nWe have a monthly and/or annual subscription business model built around patient education and treatment adherence.','Path for Chronic Disease Communities','[\"Wilmington, DE\"]','Kurbi '),('Cutting Edge is an online platform exclusive for physicians focusing on professional information. The greatest benefit of Cutting Edge to its users is that it enables them to stay on top of the latest product innovation and clinical research related to their practice anytime, anywhere. Users will receive ongoing updates on clinical research and publications, product innovation, peer-review of content, courses, events and news from their own network. Cutting Edge features a unique product directory that enables users to browse through very intuitively and find information about surgical devices and equipment they use daily. \nWe provide Cloud-based enterprise solutions, which are offered to medical device manufacturers in SaaS model, and enable them to fully control their digital content, get on-going metrics and analytics on their brands, access business intelligence, collect voice of the customer, push information about their latest innovation and streamline the work of sales reps. ','Disrupting the way surgeons and medical device companies interact.','[\"Tel Aviv-yafo\"]','Cutting Edge Surgical '),('AskNaturalHealth.ca is establishing itself as one of Canada’s largest Q&A platforms where consumers around the world can become introduced to Natural Health, Lifestyle and Product Experts on-line.  Consumers can search for Experts by a wide-array of health interests, disciplines, locations and even languages.  In a couple of easy steps they can book on-line Q&A sessions with specific Experts they want to meet and personally become introduced in a more personalized and intimate manner.','Q&A platform for natural health experts.','[\"Toronto\"]','Synnergy Group '),(