vice industry. \n\nWe make negotiating simple !\n','FoodTender.com is an online market place','[\"Shediac\"]','FoodTender Solutions Inc.'),(NULL,'','[\"Texas\"]','Elite Biomedical'),('SubroFlash is a start up which offers web based subscription access to a comprehensive record of subrogation data claim information specifically designed to provide accurate subrogation collection data to all parties of a personal injury claim. The data provides the client with the information necessary to pursue and collect the subrogation interest. The data base is an internet subscription service offering access on a monthly, quarterly or annual basis.  The company is located in Lubbock, Texas.','Internet based data base of personal injury case filings','[\"Lubbock\"]','SubroFlash'),('Established in 2002 and officially equitized in December of 2006, Worldsoft provides software solutions built to complete client specification at a fraction of the cost.  Utilizing the most up-to-date technologies, many years of high-level research and development, and a world class team of software engineers, Worldsoft can help your company achieve its targets from integrated software modules to complete turnkey systems.\n','Personalized business software. Managing your business, so you don\'t have to.','[\"Houston\"]','WorldSoft Solution Texas'),('EasyG can accurately detect the heart’s electrical fields through the application of either non-contact or contact sensors. Non-contact sensors can be attached to a patient’s clothing, saving time and preserving patient modesty. The non-contact electrodes alleviate problems associated with allergies to adhesives, burns to the skin, or excessive body hair that typically complicate the use of contact electrodes. Our dual purpose device also allows use of the contact sensors if a patient requires CPR, needs a chest tube, or is simply not wearing a shirt. Using contact sensors, it can be attached to standard sticky electrodes without the hindrance of bulky wire