ss model.\n\nAnhelo senior management is led by Mr. Alonzo Aylsworth, President and Chief Technology Officer (CTO), Mr. Tom Jones, Manager/Strategic Advisor, and Mr. Bob Mogue, Director of Sales, Marketing and Product Development. These three senior managers have over 115-years of relevant experience in this market. \n\nOur business model increases the ability of physicians to make money through more effectively diagnosing and treating obstructive sleep apnea and nasal-related diseases or maladies. Revenue will be derived from the sale of devices, test reporting, single patient use accessories and satisfying an under-served patient population that have obstructive sleep apnea.  \n','Solving Sleep Apnea ','[\"Chesterfield, MO\"]','Anhelo'),('With millions of new patients entering the healthcare system, clinics face a growing challenge of moving more patients through busy waiting rooms, fast, while also delivering quality, customized care.  The POP|M platform provides a solution that moves quality healthcare management, beyond the boundaries of traditional clinics, making it possible to deliver and manage the entire treatment process without ever requireing patients to visit a physical clinic location.\n\nAs an added solution, between visits, physicians have very little data to analyze how their patients are adjusting to new prescription treatment plans, or a means to clearly identify points of aggravation within the patients natural environment. POP|M fills this gap by aggregating and analyzing user specific data such as vitals, side effects, lab tests, and environmental impacts that may cause adverse complications or actions that may make treatment less effective.\n','POP|M - Taking Care, Beyond The Clinic.','[\"Atlanta\"]','Bynde Technologies Inc.'),('We are going to provide an alternative to the American healthcare system. Imagine combining luxurious travel with top notch healthcare! Our customer are American\'s that are looking for alternative to the current medical system. Like a medical Ebay and Priceline in one!  ','Ebay for Healthcare Solutions','[\"Los Angeles\"]','KareBid (Foundup®)'),('The stealthvape is a portable handheld aromatherapy vaporizer that can be used with a wide variety of different vaporizable substances. At only $99 with a lifetime warranty, it is one of the cheapest battery powered vaporizers on the market and is targeting a wide range of people who wish to be able to discreetly vaporize while on the go.','Portable vaporizers and medical devices.','[\"New York City\"]','Medicinal Corp'),('Iontera is pioneering new era in enhanced, pain-free and intelligent transdermal delivery of both small and large molecules. The patch uses electrical current to push drugs to the skin but because the current in our patch does not contact the skin, there is no pain or irritation typically associated with iontophoretic devices. Each patch contains a small wearable computer that can control delivery, react to input from the patient or caregiver and communicate wirelessly with other devices. ','Intelligent Transdermal Drug Delivery','[\"Providence\"]','Iontera'),('Procyrion’s minimally invasive approach to circulatory assist will provide cardiologists with a safe and effective treatment option for the 2 million US patients where no treatment currently exists. Procyrion’s device is the first catheter-deployed, long-term treatment option designed to reduce the workload of the heart and perfuse the kidneys, providing an opportunity for the heart to rest and heal. Procyrion\'s device dramatically reduces the risks associated with circulatory support devices and will, for the first time, enable treatment of younger and healthier patients before years of progressive damage occur. ','a tiny heart pump for heart failure. no surgery required.','[\"Houston\"]','Procyrion'),('SurTube: Insurance in Pediatric Enteral Care\nThis product adds 21st Century technology to a 1920\'s medical technology. A portable and reliable system for locating the end of a feeding tube no matter what setting you care for the smallest of patients. The customers are hospitals, extended care facilities and home care providers. SurTube can aid in reducing costs related to tube placement errors, improve patient outcomes, enhance healthcare provider accuracy and build an untapped revenue stream.','Assurance in Pediatric Enteral Care','[\"Chicago\"]','Cnicus '),('View Medical has designed the SurgiLight, which provides surgeons with a simple, high quality LED light that connects to existing overhead light handles. It features a long, flexible cable that will allow the user to direct the light into the cavity from any desired angle. This device delivers a bright and localized light without the burden of heavy headlamps and wired systems, and allows View Medical to offer hospitals a cost effective way to improve patient outcomes.','High quality deep cavity surgical lighting','[\"Memphis\"]','View Medical'),('Sway Balance is an FDA-cleared mobile software for postural stability and balance assessment in athletes with concussion, seniors at risk of fall, functional limitation assessments in physical therapy and tracking of neurological disease progression using only the existing hardware in any mobile device.  The Sway Balance software presents an opportunity for medical professionals to monitor patients for signs of neuromuscular and vestibular dysfunction, in a variety of medical settings, with nothing more than a smartphone or tablet device.  The portability and ease of use of our software allows the medical professional to quickly analyze a patient’s balance, as a reimbursable procedure, with a standardized protocol to develop reliable outcomes for clinical tracking.  Sway replaces subjective balance tests and expensive, immobile force platforms with a balance system that fits on the tablet you already use in your practice or on the smartphone of patients you want to remotely evaluate.','Mobile Medical Diagnostics','[\"Tulsa\"]','Sway Medical'),('MedTech Health (MTH) is a healthcare platform that addresses the needs of 1 in 2 adults. It is first online venue offering DTC opportunities to medtech manufacturers. With comprehensive multimedia-based health information, a novel social networking ecosystem and an emphasis on medtech, MTH allows users to access easy-to-understand information on health conditions and solutions. MTH also offers personalization and recommendation algorithms to customize site experience.','Online medtech DTC marketplace infused with multimedia steroids, laminar navigation & AI.','[\"Silicon Valley\"]','MedTech Health'),('In just 30 seconds the MyoVista performs a non-invasive scan that is simple, painless, cost effective, and has an 89% correlation to an expensive and invasive angiogram when identifying myocardial abnormalities. In contrast, current ECG technology only detects approximately 35% of patients with myocardial abnormalities. This is concerning when you consider that 70% of the patients with myocardial abnormalities never exhibit any symptoms, which is why it is also called Silent Heart Disease.  ','Identify Silent Heart Disease before it is Fatal','[\"Colleyville\"]','Heart Test Laboratories'),('To date, there is no objective, accurate and portable diagnostic tool to assess brain function and facilitate decision-making in the diagnosis and treatment of neurologic and neuropsychiatric conditions. As the captain of my college lacrosse team, dad of two young athletes, and former neuroscience biomarker researcher at a big pharma, I see brain injuries everywhere. This is why we launched Cerora 2 years ago, as a healthcare IT company moving concussion diagnosis from a subjective clinical impression to an objective biosensor based assessment out in the field. We are filling this diagnostic gap  with an innovative “neuro-diagnostics as a service” IT infrastructure and our multi-modal MindReader™ assessment platform. We are simplifying the system so that athletic trainers, physical therapists, nurses and medics can acquire the data at the point of care and allow the data to be remotely interpreted by a physician. We\'ve also integrated into Google Glass for GlassBrain health assessment.','Device & Software Platform for Brain Injury Detection','[\"Bethlehem, PA\"]','Cerora'),('Göobal marketplace with medical and scientific products (equipment and consumables) for professional community - medical doctors, scientists, TAs. For them the site is free to use. Customers of myQuipment are manufacturers and distributors. The publish offers for free and for unlimited time-span. Only if a product is ordered, they pay comission of 10 to 12% from the product price. The offers contain all the info specific for the market and importnat \nfor the end-users. Both sides save money and time during the process of purchasing and selling. For users: easy to compare specs, get quotation just by a mouse click, no need to visit different company sites, no distracting talks with sales-reps, learn about novel products in your field. For vendors: increase number of sales, promote your products and company name, save time on quotations, you do not need to search for customers - instead they look for your products, sell new, used, demo and discontinued equipment easily. ','Global professional marketplace for scientific & medical products (Amazon)','[\"Hamburg\"]','myQuipment'),('Ethimedix is a Swiss based medical device company featuring a proprietary biometric tamperproof drinkable drug dispenser (BTD3) assuring right dose of medication while preventing misuses, abuse and diversion.  This results in significant savings for the hospitals (more outpatient treatment) as well as reduced patients’ time to travel to hospital and doctors for medication prescription only. The first targeted clinical indication is PCA (patient controlled analgesia) for chronic pain management.\n','complex medication access platform for homecare','[\"Switzerland\"]','Ethi