kets has been limited by poor wavelength flexibility, a problem which Azur Light Systems has solved.','World\'s First Blue Laser Component','[\"Bordeaux\"]','AZUR LIGHT SYSTEMS'),('Market Intelligence for the Business Executives across the Care Continuum, viz. Healthcare, Pharma and Medical Devices. Traditionally, the Care Continuum industry has been science focused. This platform is to help business executives access relevant business intelligence for effective decision making in today\'s highly volatile industry.','Market Intelligence Platform for the Care Continuum','[\"Bangalore\"]','Bukmarker'),('InfaClip, is a patented, disposable and degradable plastic obstetric device that simultaneously cuts, clamps, and shields the infant, mother, and birthing attendant from infection, aimed at reducing maternal and neonatal mortality in developing countries.','High-quality, low-cost medical products addressing critical global health needs.','[\"New Orleans\"]','NOvate Medical Technologies'),('Medical application tools to assist medical professionals and patients.\r\nUtilizing accessible technology to help people live better, healthier lives.\r\n ','Medtech and Google Glass Colide','[\"Stanford\"]','team(evermed)'),('The WD invention relates generally to a wound-cleaning apparatus specifically designed for limbs. More particularly, its objective is to effectively attend to the limb by means of its control unit. Having devices that eliminate tasks allow for the medical personnel to seek out patients that require more immediate and manual attention. Numerous patients need care for limb wounds, which typically require the medical personnel to first clean and measure the wound. ','Medical equipment with advance high technology','[]','Lady Medical Supply INC'),('LDS provides the only passive non-contact biometric sensing system that monitors the vital signs of target individuals. This includes babies in cribs, adults with cardiovascular and related disease, residents in care fa