mote transmission of the images through commercial/military networks for remote readings and diagnoses.','Solid-state portable CT Scanner','[\"Madison\"]','Trinity Imaging Systems'),('Apaxis is developing a set of surgical tools that enable safer and easier implantation of ventricular assist devices (VADs). Our patented tools ensure that VAD implantation is more reproducible across all experience levels. Furthermore, our tools and techniques minimize the amount of blood lost, reducing overall procedure cost and mitigating post-procedural complications. Our products will drive an increase in VAD utilization by lowering costs, mitigating risk, and improving the implant experience.','Safer, easier VAD implantation','[\"Houston\"]','Apaxis Medical'),('BCISim has discovered a major advancement in diagnosis and treatment with a new technology called predictive neuro-stimulation (PNS) to detect then prevent the occurrence of seizures. Our methodology has been implemented in patients with an 86% accuracy rate in predicting Epileptic seizures before they occur in children 8-12 years old.  Our methods include finding the small, local area in the individual’s brain where initial seizure activity is measured. As this area grows and begins to take over the individual’s brain, we short-circuit this activity by sending a small electrical stimulation to the individual’s brain, thereby stopping the train of seizure pathologies.   We have developed a neuro-device to predict and reduce seizures, and we are looking for investment to increase patient testing to quickly bring our product to market.','Seizure prediction device','[\"Memphis\"]','BCISim, Inc'),('iNeuroskill is a tool that measures impairment in fine motor control by analyzing handwriting dynamics of patients suffering from Parkinson\'s Disease in real time.  This tool can be used a surrogate biomarker for Parkinson\'s Disease.','Surrogate Biomarker for Parkinson\'s Disease','[\"Boulder\"]','iNeuroskill '),('Medici’s device 