e ads via real-time bidding.','Mobile Ad Platform','[\"Palo Alto\"]','LeanMarket'),('Leftronic is a powerful dashboard builder for companies. The browser-based application makes it easy and fast to put together beautiful dashboards that connect to key metrics from services like Google Analytics, Twitter, Zendesk in real-time. The easy-to-use push API allows companies to push up their own data instantly. The sleek visual aesthetic and intuitive drag-and-drop application makes the company stand out from the competition.','Visualization-driven data analytics','[\"San Francisco\"]','Leftronic'),('Listia is a new kind of marketplace, where users trade real goods using virtual currency. We help users trade things they don\'t need anymore and get stuff they want in return. Explore: http://www.listia.com/search','online marketplace with virtual currency','[\"Silicon Valley\"]','Listia'),(NULL,'','[]','Lockitron'),('Lollipuff is an online auction site exclusively for women\'s designer clothes and accessories. Every item is pre-screened for authenticity by a team of experts (via photos alone) to ensure that no fakes ever appear on the site.  Users buy and sell new or lightly-used (aka, vintage) items directly to each other, which results in amazing prices -- up to 90% off retail.  As we like to say, Lollipuff has eBay-like prices, with the security of an upscale boutique.','eBay for Designer Goods, where every item is authenticated by brand experts','[\"San Jose\"]','Lollipuff'),('LVL6 produces next-gen mobile RPGs.\n\nOur first title, \"Age of Chaos\" has broken the Top 100 Grossing of the iOS App Store. Age of Chaos is also Kabam\'s highest grossing 3rd party title on iOS.  \n\nOur second title, \"Mobster\'s Paradise\" is set to launch mid October. ','Blizzard of the Post-PC Era (YC W12)','[\"Mountain View\"]','LVL6'),('MarketBrief transforms almost 1 million yearly SEC Filings into easy-to-understand news articles, within 1 second of their release.  Removing the reporter from market events ensures MarketBrief can break news faster than any service available and offer broader coverage including small cap and private companies.  \n\nMarketBrief is expanding to court documents, FDA, FTC, USDA, FCC, and other public sources.  MarketBrief covers 400,000 public and private companies with hundreds of paying customers.','Best source for instant and unique financial news','[]','MarketBrief'),('Markupwand converts photoshop files to beautiful HTML and CSS, like magic.\n\nIt takes care of:\n0. Maintanable and Semantic HTML\n1. Pixel perfect similarity\n2. All CSS3 candy - transforms, drop-shadow, \n3. Fits into existing CSS grids (bootstrap, blueprint, yui grids)\n4. Automatically detects web fonts from Typekit and Google webfonts and includes it.\n','Convert Photoshop files to beautiful HTML and CSS like magic (YC S12)','[\"Mountain View\"]','Markupwand'),('Matterport is developing a low-cost 3D scanner that allows anyone to quickly and easily produce a realistic 3D model.','Fast and Easy 3D Capture','[\"Mountain View\"]','Matterport'),('Medigram is a HIPAA-compliant group messaging platform for health care professionals (i.e. doctors, nurses, etc). It is cross-platform. Download the app, sign up, verify your identity, and start talking with colleagues within 60 seconds.\n\nWe bring in-hospital realtime messaging with referral communication software together under one platform.\n\nOur background is from Stanford Med and CS. We have 6+ years of hospital experience, and experience building HIPAA-compliant systems and mobile software.','HIPAA-Compliant Group Communication Platform, YC W2012, StartX F2011','[\"Los Altos\"]','Medigram'),('Medisas is cloud-based software for hospitals.\n\nOur software allows doctors and nurses to transfer really important patient information between shifts, during a process known as the \"handoff\". Deploying Medisas in a hospital significantly reduces medical errors and improves patient care. We\'re on web, desktop